\id EXO - Exodus - drafted by Pectchie in Mikarup dialect orignally; put into Ariap dialect by Siria; other translators and checkers involved in checking: Iakob, Asefi, Watarak, Steven, Joasa: comp ck by Francis and his team Oct 2012 and Oct 2013; EXO 1-24 distance ck by Norm Weatherhead and Steven and a village team, with some input from Marsha Dec 2012; face to face consultant check by Norm Weatherhead in March 2013. EXO 25-28 cons ck in progress by Martha Wade, with Francis, Martin, Michael, and Jessy in Feb 2012; EXO 29-40 cons ck by Martha Wade in Aug 2013.) 
\h Ua Me Ini 
\toc3 UMI 
\toc2 Ua Me Ini 
\toc1 God Ua Uan Gumazamiziba Inigha, Isip…®n Azenan Zui 
\mt1 God Ua Uan Gumazamiziba Inigha, Isip…®n Azenan Zui 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 Ua Me Ini 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam bar faraghav…®ra Israelia batozir bizir ekiam…®n gun m…®gei. Bizir kam, a kamak…®n. Me Isip…®n kantri ataki, kar nguazir me pura ingangarir gumaziba ko ingangarir amizir k…®nibar ikia kalabus…®n ingangarim gamizim. 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam m…®g…®r…®g…®ar akuar ekiar 3pla iti. 
\ip 1. Sapta 1 ghua 18, ak…®nafarir akuar faragha zuim, an Israelia Isip…®n kantri ategha f…®riagh…®regha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghua Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n otozir darorim geghari. 
\ip 2. Sapta 19 ghua 24, ak…®nafarir akuar kam, God Israelia ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gamigha, an akar gavgaviba me gan…®ga men sure gami, eght…® me uan daroriba ko araziba derav…®ra dar ganam. 
\ip 3. Sapta 25 ghua 40, ak…®nafarir akuar kam…®n aven, Israelia God…®n Purirpenim…®n ingari. Egha God…®n ziam fer araziba ko akar igharaziba iti. Egha uaghan ofa gamir gumazibar ingangarim damuamin m…®g…®r…®g…®aba an iti. 
\ip Faraghav…®ra zuir gumazir ekiam Moses, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven iti. God uab…® gumazir dapanim…®n ik…® Isipia da ua Israelia iniasa a ginaba. 
\ip Nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamizir av…®rim, God Israelia gan…®ngizir 10plan Akar Gavgavibagh fos. Akar Gavgavir kaba, sapta 20…®n iti. 
\ip God uab…® amizir biziba dar m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ak…®nafarir kam…®n faraghav…®ra iti. God uab…® Israelian apaniba da, ua me ini. God uab…® me gamiz…® me ik…®zir vam…®ra ikia ziar ekiam iti, egha me an gumazamizibara ikiasa a me ginaba. God uab…® me geghuva gavgavim me gan…®di. Eght…® me ingangarir ekiar God ifongezibar amuam. 
\c 1  
\ms1 God ingangarim isa Moses gan…®ngi 
\mr (Sapta 1--4) 
\s1 Isipia pazav…®ra Israelia gami 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1-4 \xt Jenesis 46:8-27\x*Jekop…®n otariba an g…®n Isip…®n kantrin ghu, me uan adarazi sara, men ziabar kara:  
\v 2-4 Ruben, Simeon, Livai, Juda, Isakar, Sebulun, Benjamin, Dan, Naptali, Gat ko Aser.  
\v 5 Josep men faraghav…®ra ghugha Isip…®n iti. Gumazamizir kaba me Jekop…®n otivizir ovavir boriba. Me bar men d…®bobonim 70…®n ghu. 
\p  
\v 6 Dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma, Josep, ko an aveghbuaba bar, ko gumazamizir dughiar m…®taghniar kam…®n ikeziba, me bar ariaghire.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Aposel 7:17\x*Ez…® Israel…®n gumazamiziba borir av…®rim batima, men av…®rim bar ekevegha bar av…®rasemegha gavgavigha Isip…®n kantri bar a giz…®fa. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Aposel 7:18\x*Azenir av…®ribar g…®n, atrivir igiar mam Isip…®n kantrin atrivim…®n oto. Atrivir kam Josep g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 9 Egha a uan gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIsraelian gumazamiziba bar av…®raseme, ez…® men av…®rim ko gavgavim bar en av…®rim ko gavgavim gafira.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Aposel 7:19\x*Eght…® m…®dorozim otoght…®, me ti en apaniba ko uari akuvagh e ko m…®sogh…®va, en kantri ategh aregham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e tuavitam batogh me damight…®, me ot…®v arogh av…®rasemeghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Kamagh…®n Isipian atrivim uan apengan ingarir gumaziba ko, me ingangarim…®n ganamin gumazir maba m…®sevegha, ingangarim me gan…®ngi. Men ingangarir kam, a kamak…®n, me puv…®ra Israelia ab…®n me damut…®, me bar os…®mt…®zir dafaba sara ingangarir ekiabar amuam. Me Israelia gamima me nguibar ekiar pumuning…®n ingari, Pitom…®n nguibam ko Rameses…®n nguibamning, kar nguibar ekiar atrivim…®n daghebar ar…®ghamimning.\f + \fr 1:11 \ft Pitom ko Rameses…®n nguibar ekiamning, me aning ingarigha, atrivim…®n dagher d…®penir dafaba aning…®n aven ingari. Ez…® Isipia dagheba otevir dughiam…®n araravim gamua dagher av…®rim aning gar…®si.\f* 
\v 12 Isipia bar pazav…®ra Israelia gamima, me uaghan bar av…®rasemegha Isip gizefi. Me kamagh…®n me gamua ghuav…®ra iti me puv…®ra ingarava, boriba bata ghuav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Isipia men atiatia bar men aghua.  
\v 13 Isipia me gamima, me puv…®ra ingarava, os…®mt…®zir ekiaba ateri, Isipia tong men apangkuvir pu. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 14 Egha Isipia puv…®ra me ab…®ra me gamima, me brighbar ingara d…®penibar ingarava uaghan azenibar obarir ingangaribagh ami. Ez…® ik…®r…®m…®rim bar men as…®ghas…®ki. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Isip…®n atrivim, Sifra ko Puan dia, aning Hibrun amizir otasava amibar, akurvazir amizimning. Egha an akar gavgavim aning gan…®ga, ghaze,  
\v 16 ‚ÄúGua Hibrun amizir otasava amibar akurvagh…®va gan, amizim otarim bateght…®, gua a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. A borir guivim bateght…®, gua aneteght…® a ik…®.‚Äù  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Ua Me Ini 1:21\x*Ez…® amizir kamning God…®n atiatiava Isip…®n atrivim aning m…®kemez…® mogh…®n amir puvat…®, egha otariba atagh…®razima me iti. 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Isip…®n atrivim aning…®n diagha aning…®n azara, ‚ÄúGua tizim bagha otariba ataghiz…®ma me iti?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® amizimning kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúHibrun amiziba Isipian amizibar m…®n amir puvat…®, me amizir gavgaviba. Me ot…®s…®, me bar zuam…®ra otegham, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ga t…®ghar magh…®n mang…®t…® me otegh g…®vagham.‚Äù  
\v 20-21 Amizir kamning God…®n atiati, kamagh…®n amiz…® God deragha aning gamima aning uaghan uaning bagha boriba bati. Kamagh…®n Israel…®n gumazamiziba bar otava arogha ghuav…®ra ikia gavgafi. 
\p  
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Aposel 7:19\x*Ez…® g…®n atrivim kamagh…®n Isip…®n gumazamiziba bar me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Hibrun otarir iririviba is…®, Nail…®n Fanem…®n me akunigh. Egh guivir iririviba ateght…®, me ik…®.‚Äù 
\c 2  
\s1 Moses iririvimra itima, me a m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…® 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n Livain ovavir borir gumazir mam, a Livain ovavir borir amizir mam…®n iti.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Aposel 7:20; Hibru 11:23\x*G…®n amizir kam navim asegha otarir mam bate. Egha an an garima, an ganganim bar dera, kamagh…®n amiz…® a 3plan iak…®nibar a modi.  
\v 3 An amebam uam a mongan asaghava, ak…®rar me ighurunibar m…®n garir grazir aghuibar ingarizir mam inigha, koltan an toriba ap…®ri. Eght…® d…®pam aven mangan kogham. Egha borim aven anet…®gha ghua Nail…®n Faner m…®riam…®n grazibar tong…®n d…®pam gis…®n anet…®.  
\v 4 Ez…® borim…®n amezemebam mong saghuiam…®n tugha modogha an gari, bizir tizitam a bativam. 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® atrivim…®n guivim ruasa fanem…®n uaghirima, an ingangarir amiziba an g…®n ghua d…®par m…®riam…®n arui. Ez…® atrivim…®n guivim amuaviava ak…®rar kam grazibar tong…®n an apigha, a iniasa ingangarir amizir mam amada.  
\v 6 Egha atrivim…®n guivim ak…®rar kam…®n asuam kuigha otarim…®n garima, an araima, an an apangkufi. Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar Hibrubar borir mam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® an amezemebam izava an azai, ‚ÄúK…® mang…®va Hibrun amizitam m…®kemeght…®, a n…® bagh oteba a dan…®ngam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® atrivim…®n guivim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAria, n…® m…®gei mogh…®n damu.‚Äù Ez…® guivim ghua borim…®n amebamra inigha ize. 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® atrivim…®n guivim amizir kam kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® borir kam inigh na bagh a damu oteba a dan…®ngt…®, k…® n…® givezam.‚Äù Ez…® amizir kam borim inigha a bagha a gamua oteba a gan…®di. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Aposel 7:21\x*G…®n borir kam ekevez…®ma, an amebam a inigha atrivim…®n guivim bagha ghu. Ez…® atrivim…®n guivim, otarir kam, mati an otozir borim…®n m…®rara ua bagha a gami. Egha a kamagh…®n uab…® m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® d…®pam…®n a isava azenim gat…®. Kamagh…®n, k…® ziam, Moses, a dar…®gham.‚Äù\f + \fr 2:10 \ft Hibrun akam…®n, ziar kam, ‚ÄúMoses,‚Äù akar kam…®n m…®rara ghu, ‚ÄúA inigh p…®n anang.‚Äù\f* 
\s1 Moses ara Midian kantrin ghu 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Hibru 11:24\x*\x - \xo 2:11-14 \xt Aposel 7:23-28\x*Ez…® g…®n Moses aghuigha gumazim aragha g…®vagha, atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n azenan ghua Hibrubar ganasa zui, kar an akar gumazamiziba. A ghua men garima, Isipia ingangarir os…®mt…®zibar amuasa puv me ab…®ri. A uaghan garima, Isipian mav Hibrun mav m…®sosi, kar an akar gumazir mam.  
\v 12 Ez…® Moses tintinibar garima, tav itir puvat…®z…®, a Isip…®n gumazir kam m…®suegha an kuam gigim…®n aven a modo. 
\p  
\v 13 Egha an am…®mzaraghan uamategha ghua garima, Hibrun gumazimning uaning m…®sosi. Ez…® a m…®dorozim forezir gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha uan akar gumazim m…®sosi?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® gumazir kam a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúTina n…® am…®sevez…® n…® en gumazir dapanim ko jas…®n ikiava en gari? N…® Isipian gumazim m…®soghez…® an aremez…® mogh…®n, n…® na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghasa, a?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n oregha atiatigha, kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúK…® amizir bizir kam, gumazamiziba a g…®fo.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Aposel 7:29; Hibru 11:27\x*Ez…® Isip…®n atrivim g…®n Moses amizir bizir kam baregha, Moses m…®sueght…® an aremeghasava ami. Ez…® kamagh…®n Moses atrivim…®n ara ghua, Midian…®n nguazim…®n oto. Egha mozir d…®par mam…®n m…®riam…®n aperaghav iti.  
\v 16 Midian…®n nguazim…®n, ofa gamir gumazir mam, an ziam Jetro. A 7pla guiviba iti. Ez…® dughiar kam, an guiviba iza mozir pam tuigha uan afeziam…®n sipsipba ko memebar an…®ngasa, itarir bar ekiam gingasava ami.  
\v 17 Ez…® sipsipbar garir gumazir maba iza Jetron guiviba, me batosi. Ez…® Moses guivibar akuragha gumazir kaba munamadagha, d…®pam tuigha Jetron sipsipba ko memebagh an…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® me uamategha zuima men afeziam men azara, ‚ÄúManmagh amiz…® ia zuam…®ra uamatenge?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIsip…®n gumazir mam en akuragha sipsipbar garir gumaziba munamada. Egha d…®pam tuigha en sipsipba ko memebagh an…®ngi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® afeziam men azara, ‚ÄúGumazir kam managh iti? Ia tizim bagha anetegha ize? Ia mang…®va a m…®kemeght…® a iz…®va, e ko dam…®.‚Äù Ez…® me ghua Moses inigha izi. 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Moses Jetro ko ikiasa ifonge. Ez…® Jetro uan guivim Sipora, Moses…®n ikiasava a gan…®ngi.  
\v 22 Ez…® Sipora otarim batez…®, Moses kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® nguibar igharazim…®n gumazim…®n m…®n iza ia ko iti, kamagh…®n k…® ziam Gersom a gat…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 2:22 \ft Hibrun akam…®n, ziar kam, ‚ÄúGersom,‚Äù akar kam…®n m…®rara ghu, ‚Äúnguibar igharazim…®n gumazim.‚Äù\f* 
\p  
\v 23 Dughiar ruarim g…®vaz…®ma, Isip…®n atrivim areme. Ez…® Isipia Israelia me gativagha men gari, me puv…®ra ingara os…®mt…®zir kaba isav…®ra ikiava, akurvazim bagha pamtem…®n arai, ‚ÄúO God, en akuragh.‚Äù Ez…® men ararem God bagha ghuavanabo.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Jenesis 15:13-14\x*Ez…® God men ararem baregha Abraham ko, Aisak ko, Jekop ko, amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gin…®r…®.  
\v 25 Kamagh…®n God, Israel…®n gumazamizibar garima men ik…®r…®m…®rim bar ikufi, ez…® a men apangkuvigha, men akurvaghasa n…®ghn…®si. 
\c 3  
\s1 God Moses…®n dia 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar mam…®n Moses uan amerem Jetron sipsipba ko memebagh eghuva, da inigha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganir mam…®n ghua, a ifagha vong…®n ghua Horep…®n oto, kar God baghav…®ra itir m…®ghs…®am. Horep…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n ziar igharazim, Sainai.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2-10 \xt Aposel 7:30-34\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel temer otevir mam…®n aguabar tong…®n avir m…®zariabar aven, puram a bato. Ez…® Moses temer otevir kam…®n gari, avim isia daforofozima, temem isir puvat…®.  
\v 3 Ez…® Moses aguaghfagha ghaze, ‚ÄúKar bizir igharazim! Tizim bagha temer kam isir puvat…®? K…® rogh…®ra mang…® an ganigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Moses…®n gari a rogh…®ra izima, God temem…®n aguabar tong…®n ikia an dia, ‚ÄúMoses! Moses!‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Moses a ikara, ‚ÄúK…® kati.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® God ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® rogh…®ra izan mark…®! Nguazir n…® is…®n tughav tir kam, kar anogoroghezir nguazim, a nan nguazimra. Kamagh…®n n…® uan dagarir asuaba suegh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Egha God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® n…®n afeziam…®n God. Egha uaghan n…®n inazir afeziaba, Abraham, Aisak ko Jekop…®n God.‚Äù Ez…® Moses God…®n akam baregha, an ganan atiatigha uan guam avara. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra gari, nan gumazamiziba Isip…®n kantrin ikia, men ik…®r…®m…®rim bar ikufi. Egha k…® me barazi, me ingangarim…®n garir gumazir kurabar atiatia, nan akurvazim bagha arai. Ez…® k…® bar men os…®mt…®zibagh fogha men apangkufi.  
\v 8 Egh k…® Isipian dafarim da ua me inigh men akuraghasa izaghiri. Egh Isipian nguazim…®n men aku, nguazir ekiar aghuim…®n mangam, nguazir kam a bar deraz…®, biziba an ikiava bar deraghav…®ram aghui. Nguazir kam, Kenania, Hitia, Amoria, Peresia, Hivia ko Jebusia, dat…®r…®gh…®n a gapiaghav iti.  
\v 9 Ez…® nan gumazamiziba, k…® men ararem baregha, Isipia pazav…®ra me gamir arazibar ganigha g…®fa.  
\v 10 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® n…® amadi. Eght…® n…® Isipian atrivim bagh mang…®t…® a n…®n amamangat…®ght…®, n…® nan gumazamiziba inigh Isip…®n kantri ategh…®va azenan izam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n God m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® gavgaviba ko ziaba puvat…®zir gumazim. Guizbang…®ra, k…® atrivim bagh mang…®va Israelia inigh Isip ategh azenan izan iburaghburaki.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® God a ikara, ‚ÄúK…® n…® ko ikiam. N…® gumazamiziba inigh Isip…®n azenan iz…®va m…®ghs…®ar kam…®n nan ziam fam. Bizir kam n…® damight…® n…® fogham, k…® n…® amada.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Ua Me Ini 6:2-3\x*Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Israelia bagh mang…® me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIan ovavibar God ia bagha na amada,‚Äô eght…® me nan azaragham, ‚ÄòAn ziam tina?‚Äô Eght…® k…® manmagh…®n me m…®k…®mam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Akar Mogomem 1:4; 1:8\x*Ez…® God Moses m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…®rara, K…® Uab…® K…® Kamagh…®ra Iti. N…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòK…®rara K…® Uab…®, kar God…®n ziam, egha a ia bagha na amada.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Egha God ua kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n Israelian gumazamizibav k…®m, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, a ian inazir afeziabar God, an Abraham ko Aisak ko Jekop…®n God, a na amadaz…®, k…® ia bagha izi.‚Äô Ziar kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a zurazurara nan ziam, ez…® g…®n otivamin boriba ziar kamra na d…®pon.\f + \fr 3:15 \ft Hibrun akam…®n, me, God…®n ziar a Moses m…®kemezim, kamagh…®n an osiri, ‚ÄúYhwh.‚Äù Fofozir gumaziba deragha ziar kam d…®borir arazim g…®fozir puvat…®, egha gumazir av…®rir maba ghaze, e kamagh…®n a d…®ponam, ‚ÄúYave.‚Äù Hibrun akam…®n aven, akar kam mong an m…®rara ghu, ‚ÄúK…® uab…® k…® kamagh…®ra ikiav…®ra iti,‚Äù o ‚ÄúK…® zurara kamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù (N…® ves 14…®n gan.) Hibruia God…®n ziar kam, gumazamiziba a d…®ponan me bar anogoroke. Me ak…®nafarim…®n an osiri, egha dughiar me a d…®ponamim, me ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam.‚Äù Ez…® Tok Pisin Buk Baibel…®n aven, e ghaze, ‚ÄúEkiam,‚Äù o Bikpela. Ez…® Aruam…®n Akam…®n aven, e ziar kam ‚ÄúYave,‚Äù an m…®ngarim…®n g…®n ghua, egha ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God,‚Äù d…®bori. Egha vez…®n manam ziar kam ‚ÄúYhwh,‚Äù an iti, e kamagh…®n an osiri, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù Kamak…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a God…®n ziam.\f* 
\v 16 N…® mang…®va Israel…®n gumazir dapaniba akuvagh me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, a ian ovaviba, Abraham, Aisak ko Jekop…®n God, a na batogha, kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® ian garima, Isipia pazav…®ra ia gami.  
\v 17 K…® ia inigh Isip…®n kantrin azenan mangasa m…®kemegha g…®fa, kantrin kam me pazav…®ra ia gami. Egh k…® ia inigh nguazir aghuim…®n mangam. Nguazir kam a bar deraz…®, biziba an ikiava bar deraghav…®ram aghui. Nguazir kam, Kenania, Hitia, Amoria, Peresia, Hivia ko Jebusia dat…®r…®gh…®n a gapiagha iti.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúEght…® Israel…®n gumazir dapaniba n…® baraght…®, n…® me inigh Isip…®n atrivim bagh mang…®va kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, a Hibruian God, a iza e bato. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n en amamangat…®ght…®, e 3plan aruebar mang…® gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…®gh…®va, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, e an ofa damuam.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 19 ‚ÄúK…® kamagh…®n fo, Isip…®n atrivim ian amamangat…®ghan kogh mang…®, a gant…® nan gavgavim an gavgavim gafiragham. Eght…® a dughiar kam…®n ian amamangat…®ght…®, ia mangam.  
\v 20 K…® uan gavgavim…®n Isipia gas…®ghas…®gh, mirakel…®n igharagha garir av…®ribar amuam. Bizir kabar g…®n, a ia ateght…®, ia mangam. 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 3:21-22 \xt Ua Me Ini 12:35-36\x*‚ÄúK…® Isipia damut…® me ia gifuegham, eght…® ia mangamin dughiam…®n, ia dafarir k…®nibar mangan kogham.  
\v 22 Israelian amiziba bar vaghvagh mang…®, uarir borogh…®ra itir Isipian amizibar d…®penibar mang…®, egh uaghan pura amizir uan adarazir d…®penibar aven akuiba, korotiaba ko gol ko silvan kurkaziba bagh men azangs…®gh. Eght…® g…®n Israelia bizir kabar uan otariba ko guivibar kurkiam. Tuavir kam…®n ia Isipian bizir aghuiba pura da inigh mangam.‚Äù 
\c 4  
\s1 God mirakelbar amuamin gavgavim Moses gan…®ngi 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Moses God ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIsraelian gumazir dapaniba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ikian kogh, bizir k…® me m…®geiba baraghan kogh, egh suam, ‚ÄòN…® na batozir puvat…®,‚Äô eght…® k…® manmagh…®n damuam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® tizim uan dafarim…®n an suiraghav iti?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Moses ghaze, ‚ÄúAghorir asadivim.‚Äù 
