\v 5 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n damight…® Israelia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…® kamagh…®n fogham, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a men ovavibar God, an Abraham ko Aisak ko Jekop…®n God, a n…® bato.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan dafarim uan evarim gis…®n korotiam…®n aven amadagh.‚Äù Ez…® Moses uan dafarim uan evarim gis…®n korotiam…®n aven amadaghava uam anesi, ez…® ar…®mariam lepa an dafarim bato, egha a ghuariam…®n m…®n ghurghuri. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan dafarim ua uan evarim gis…®n korotiam…®n aven anemadagh.‚Äù Ez…® Moses God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami, egha a ua uan dafarim asiz…®, an dafarim ua deragha an m…®karzim…®n m…®rara gari. 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…®n ikian kogh, egh mirakel…®n n…® faraghava amizim…®n ganigh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikian koght…®, mirakel…®n kamnang me damight…®, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikiam.  
\v 9 Egh me mirakel…®n arazir kamning…®n ganigh, egh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikian kogh, egh n…®n akam baraghan koght…®, n…® Nail…®n Fanem…®n mang…® d…®patam tuigh nguazim gingegh. Eght…® d…®par n…® nguazim gingezim, ghuzim…®n otogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Moses Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúMark…®, Ekiam. N…® na amangan mark…®. K…® fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n deragha bizibav geir puvat…®. Ez…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n na m…®geima, k…® bizibav geir gumazim…®n m…®n otozir puvat…®. K…® asoghosogha bizibav g…®a, egha uaghan n…®m…®ra bizibav gei. Egha k…® m…®k…®mamin n…®ghn…®zitam zuam…®ra a gin…®r…®ghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúTina gumazim…®n akam…®n ingari? Tina a gamima, an kuariba a bangani, o a m…®geir puvat…®? Tina a gamima, a gari, o an damaziba an okafi? Kar k…®rara, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® bizir kabagh ami da otifi.  
\v 12 Ez…® n…® mang…®. K…® n…®n akuraght…®, n…® m…®k…®mam. K…® n…® m…®k…®mt…®, n…® m…®k…®mam.‚Äù 
