\v 15 Eght…® g…®n n…® a geghan…®va a m…®k…®mamin bizibar a m…®k…®m. K…® guan akuraght…®, gua m…®k…®mam. Egh bizir manaba, k…® gua m…®k…®mt…®, gua fofozim inigh dar amuam.  
\v 16 A n…®n bizibav k…®mamin gumazim, egh a n…® bagh gumazamizibav k…®mam. Egh an n…®ghn…®zim…®n a n…®n akatorim…®n m…®n ikiam. Egha an damazim…®n, n…® mati an god…®n m…®n ikiam.  
\v 17 Egh n…® uan dafarim…®n aghorir asadivir kam…®n suiragh mang…®. Egh n…® g…®n aghorir asadivir kam…®n mirakelbar amuam.‚Äù 
\s1 Moses uamategha Isip…®n ghu 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Moses uamategha uan amerem Jetro bagha ghugha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGa uaning, n…® na teght…® k…® uamategh Isip…®n mang…®gh uan adarazir ganika, me ti ikiav…®ra ikiama?‚Äù 
\p Ez…®, Jetro an amamangat…®gha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAria, n…® navir averiar am…®rizim sara mang…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Moses Midianra ikiav…®ra itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIsipian gumazir n…® m…®soghasava amiba, me ariaghire. Kamagh…®n, n…® uamategh Isip…®n mang…®.‚Äù  
\v 20 Ez…® Moses uan amuim ko otarir pumuning donki dafagha, asadivir aghorir God iniasa a m…®kemezir kam, uan dafarim…®n an suiragha, d…®kavigha Isip…®n zui. 
\p  
\v 21 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua Moses kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uamategh Isip…®n mang…®gh…®va, atrivim…®n damazim…®n mirakelbar amu. K…® mirakelbar amuamin gavgavim n…® gan…®ngi. Egh k…® atrivim…®n navim damight…® a gavgavigham, eght…® a Israelian amamangat…®ght…®, me mang…®ghan kogham.  
\v 22 Eght…® n…® kamagh…®n atrivim m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n n…® m…®gei, ‚ÄúIsrael nan otarir ivariam.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 4:23 \xt Ua Me Ini 12:29\x*Ez…® k…® n…® m…®gei, N…® nan otarim ateght…® a mang…®va nan ofa damuam. Egh n…® an anogoreght…®, a mang…®ghan koght…®, kamagh…®n, k…® n…®n otarir ivariam m…®sueght…® an aremegham.‚Äù ‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® Moses uan amuiroghboriba ko Isip…®n zuima, am…®nim p…®rima me tuavir ar…®zim…®n avughsazir danganir mam…®n iti. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses batogha a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasava ami.\f + \fr 4:24 \ft Moses uan otarim…®n m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim atuzir puvat…®. Bizir kam bang…®n God a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa.\f* 
\v 25 Ez…® Moses…®n amuim Sipora dag…®ar ghumt…®zir mam inigha uan otarim…®n m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim atugha, Moses…®n dagarimning gat…®gha, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGhuzir kam bang…®n, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n na ko ga poroghamimning.‚Äù  
\v 26 Dughiar kam Sipora m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim aghorir arazim g…®n…®ghn…®gha egha ghaze, ‚ÄúGhuzir kam bang…®n, ga poroghamimning…®n oto.‚Äù Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n ganigha Moses ataghiz…® a ikia egha, aremezir puvat…®.\f + \fr 4:26 \ft Moses…®n amuim Sipora, an danganim inigha otarim…®n nir mogomem atu. Kamagh…®n God anetaghiz…® a iti.\f* 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Aron m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…®va Moses batogh.‚Äù Ez…® Aron d…®kavigha ghua God…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n otogha, Moses batogha an tore.  
\v 28 Ez…® Moses bar Aron kamagh…®n a geghara ghaze, God akaba na gan…®ngigha egha Isip…®n mang…®va dar gun m…®k…®masa na amada. Egha God mirakelba nan akagha ghaze, k…® mang…® Isip…®n dar amuam. 
