\v 30 Ez…® Aron Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®kemezir biziba bar dar gun me m…®g…®a, egha uaghan mirakelba gumazamizibar damazim…®n dagh ami.  
\v 31 Ez…® me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti. Me kamagh…®n oraki, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me bagha iza men garima, Isipia pazav…®ra me gamima, a me bagha n…®ghn…®gha men apangkufi. Kamagh…®n, me teviba ap…®righa, dapaniba avigha nguazim…®n gara an ziam fe. 
\c 5  
\ms1 God ua Isipia da Israelia ini 
\mr (Sapta 5:1--15:21) 
\s1 Moses ko Aron Isip…®n atrivim…®n ganasa zui 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Moses ko Aron Isip…®n atrivim bagha ghugha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® nan gumazamiziba ateght…® me mang…®, egh isatam gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n a damuva nan ziam fam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® atrivim ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a tina? K…® tizim bagh a baregh Israelia ateght…® me mangam? K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®fozir puvat…®, kamagh…®n k…® Israelia ateght…® me mang…®ghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Moses ko Aron ghaze, ‚ÄúHibruian God, a izava e bato. Kamagh…®n, e uari n…® en amamangat…®ght…®, e aruer 3plan gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, e uan God…®n ofa damuam. E kamagh…®n damighan koght…®, an ar…®mariar kuram o m…®dorozir ekiam…®n e damigh e m…®sueght…® e ar…®ghiregham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® atrivim Moses ko Aron m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGua manmagh n…®ghnigha gumazamiziba men ingangarim…®n men anogorosi? Gua uan ingangarim bagh uamategh mang…®.  
\v 5 Gua gan, Isip…®n aven Israelia bar av…®raseme, ez…® gua ingangarim damuan men anogorosi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6-7 Egha dughiar kamra, Isipian gumazir kurar ingangaribar gariba ko, Israelian gumazir men apengan ingariba, atrivim me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ami mogh…®n grazir m…®diarir brighbar ingariba is…® Israelian dan…®ngan mark…®. Me uari mang…® graziba iniam.\f + \fr 5:6-7 \ft Israelia kantri Isip…®n ikia brighbar ingarir arazim kamagh…®n ghu. Me grazir m…®diarir otevir muziariba inigh, d…®pam itir beghneazim sara da veregh, brighbar m…®n da aghoregh, da is…® aruem o avim dat…®ght…® da m…®sigh gavgavigham.\f* 
\v 8 Ia me m…®k…®mt…®, me brighbar ingart…®, dar d…®bobonim faragha iti mogh…®ra kamagh…®ra ik…®. D…®bobonir kam is…®vagh mag…®ran mark…®. Bar mark…®. Me am…®ragha egha ghaze, e ateght…® e gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…®gh uan God…®n ofa damuam.  
\v 9 Ia ingangarir av…®riba me dan…®ng, egh me damut…®, me bar puv…®ram ingar, egh ifavarir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba baraghamin dughiaba puvat…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Isipian ingangarim…®n garir gumazir kuraba ko men apengan itir ingangarim…®n garir gumaziba azenan ghua kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim ghaze, ‚ÄòE ua graziba ia dan…®ngan kogham.  
\v 11 Ia uan gavgavibar tintinibar mang…® graziba iniva, brigh…®n av…®ribar ingart…® dar d…®bobonim faragha ikez…® mogh…®ra ik…®.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Kamagh…®n Israelian gumazamiziba graziba buriasa tintinibar ghua, Isip…®n nguibam…®n danganibar grazir otevir muziariba buri.  
\v 13 Ez…® ingangarim…®n garir gumazir kuraba men av…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúE faragha graziba ia gan…®ngiz…® ia brighbar ingariz…® mogh…®ra, dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiaba bar kamagh…®ra ingar.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Isipian ingangarim…®n garir gumazir kuraba faragha Israelian gumazir maba, men apengan ingangarim…®n garir gumaziba me am…®sefe. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n me me bagha ghua, puv me m…®sogha me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúManmaghsuav…®ra ia dat…®r…®gh…®n ingarizir brigh…®n d…®bobonim, ia faragha ingariz…® d…®bobonim…®n m…®n otozir puvat…®?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Israelian ingangaribar garir gumaziba ghua uari bagha atrivim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® manmaghsua kamagh…®n e n…®n ingangarir gumaziba e gami?  
\v 16 Me graziba e gan…®ngizir puvat…®gha, brighbar ingarasa puram e m…®gei. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n e m…®sosi. Kar en os…®mt…®zim puvat…®. Ia Isipia, kar ian os…®mt…®zimra.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa puram am…®ragha ingangarim…®n aghua! Egha ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® en amamangat…®ght…®, e mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damuam.‚Äô  
\v 18 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®ra uamategh uan ingangarim damus…® mang…®! Me grazitaba ia danighan kogham. Eght…® ia brigh…®n d…®bobonir me ia m…®kemezir kam, ia dar ingaright…® da otifigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Israelian ingangarim…®n garir gumazir me m…®seveziba orazi, atrivim brigh…®n d…®bobonim otevegh izighiran an anogoroke. Ez…® me fo, dat…®r…®gh…®n os…®mt…®zir dafam me bato.  
\v 20 Egha me atrivim…®n danganim ategha ghua Moses ko Aron bato. Aning me m…®zua iti.  
\v 21 Egha ingangarim…®n garir gumaziba kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua e gamiz…® dat…®r…®gh…®n e mati atrivim ko an gumazir dapanibar atinim…®n mughuriam at…®. Egha me e m…®soght…® e ovengamin tuavim ak…®righa g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God guan arazir kam…®n ganigha g…®fa, egh guan arazir kam…®n ivezir kuram gua dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\s1 Moses…®n navim bar osemez…® a God ko m…®gei 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Moses uam Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ghua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® manmaghsua uan gumazamiziba arazir kurar kam…®n me gami? Egha n…® tizim baghav…®ra na amadaz…®ma, k…® kagh ize?  
\v 23 K…® n…®n akaba inigha ghua atrivim m…®kemezir dughiam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, atrivim arazir kurabar me gami. Ez…® n…® men akurvaghasa bizitam gamizir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® dat…®r…®gh…®n mang…® bizir k…® atrivim damuamim…®n ganam. K…® uan gavgavim…®n a damight…®, a nan gumazamiziba ateght…® me mangam. Guizbang…®ra, k…® uan gavgavim…®n pamten ingar, pamten a m…®k…®mt…® a uan kantrin me batueght…®, me mangam.‚Äù 
\s1 God ua Moses m…®gei 
\p  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2-3 \xt Jenesis 17:1; 28:3; 35:11; Ua Me Ini 3:13-15\x*Egha God kamagh…®n Moses m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® uab…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.  
\v 3 Azenir bar faragha ghua g…®vazibar, k…® Abraham ko Aisak ko Jekop, me batifi. Ez…® me fo, k…® Gavgaviba Bar Itir God. Egha k…® uan ziam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an gun me m…®kemezir puvat…®. Me ziar kam g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 4 Egha k…® uaghan uan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim me ko anek…®righa ghaze, k…® Kenanian nguazim me dan…®ngam. Nguazir me itir kam, kar men nguazim puvat…®.  
\v 5 Isipia dat…®r…®gh…®n Israelia gamiz…®, me ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar ikia, tuava ararer dafam gami. Ez…® k…® men ararem baregha, uan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gin…®r…®. 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúN…® nan akam is…® Israelia me dan…®ng, ‚ÄòK…® uab…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. K…® Isipian dafarim da ia iniva os…®mt…®zir me ia gar…®ziba da ia inigh, egh ia damight…® ia f…®righ…®regham. Egh k…® uan gavgavim…®n ivezir kuram me dan…®ng, egh ian akuragh ua ia iniam.  
\v 7 Egh k…® ia damight…® ia nan gumazamizibar ik…®t…®, k…® ian God…®n m…®n ikiam. Egh k…® g…®n ia damight…® ia Isipian ingangarir arazim…®n f…®righ…®regh, dughiar kam…®n ia fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God.  
\v 8 K…® ia inigh mang…® nguazir kam…®n otogham, nguazir kam, k…® faragha Abraham, Aisak ko Jekop, me ko akam ak…®rizir nguazim. K…® ia danight…®, a ian nguazim…®n m…®n ikiam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù  
\v 9 Ez…® Moses akar kam…®n Israelia m…®keme. Ez…® men ingangarir m…®zazim men n…®ghn…®ziba ab…®ni. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, me Moses…®n akam barazir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 10-11 Ez…® g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Isip…®n atrivim m…®kemeght…®, a Israelia ateght…® me an kantri ategh mang…®.‚Äù  
\v 12 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIsraelia nan akam barazir puvat…®. Ez…® atrivim manmagh…®n na baragham? Na m…®zem na basemez…®, k…® deragha bizibav geir puvat…®. Egh k…® manmagh…®n deragh atrivim m…®k…®mam?‚Äù  
\v 13 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Moses ko Aron Israelia inigh Isip…®n azenan mangasa, akar gavgavim aning ganigha aning amadaz…®, aning Israelia m…®k…®m egh Isip…®n atrivim m…®k…®masa zui. 
\s1 Moses ko Aron…®n ik…®zim…®n ziaba 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Ruben a Jekop…®n otarir ivariam, an otarir 4pla bate, Hanok, Palu, Hesron, ko Karmi. 4plan otarir kaba, me vaghvagha uan ik…®zibar inazir afeziabar otifi. Ez…® men ik…®ziba vaghvagha men ziaba ini. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Simeon otarir 6pla iti, Jemuel, Jamin, Ohat, Jakin, Sohar, ko Saul, kar Kenanian amizim…®n otariba. Otarir kaba, me vaghvagha uan ik…®zibar inazir afeziabar otifi. Ez…® men ik…®ziba vaghvagha men ziaba ini.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16-19 \xt D…®boboniba 3:17-20; 26:57-58; 1 Eghaghaniba 6:16-19\x*Ez…® Livai otarir 3pla iti, Gerson, Kohat, ko Merari. Otarir kaba, me vaghvagha uan ik…®zibar inazir afeziabar otifi. Ez…® men ik…®ziba vaghvagha men ziaba ini. Ez…® Livai azenir 137plan ikegha areme.  
\v 17 Ez…® Gerson otarir pumuning iti, Lipni, ko Simei. Ez…® g…®n aning vaghvagha uan ik…®zimning…®n dapanimning…®n oto.  
\v 18 Ez…® Kohat otarir 4pla iti, Amram, Ishar, Hebron, ko Usiel. Egha Kohat azenir 133plan ikegha areme.  
\v 19 Ez…® Merari otarir pumuning iti, Mali ko Musi. Gumazir kaba bar, men ovavir boriba sara, me Livain anabam…®n aven itir adarasi. 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® Amram uan afeziam…®n buaramizim Jokebet…®n itima, an a bagha Aron ko Moses bate. Ez…® Amram azenir 137plan ikegha areme.  
\v 21 Ez…® Ishar otarir 3pla iti, Kora, Nefek, ko Sikri.  
\v 22 Ez…® Usiel otarir 3pla iti, Misael, Elsafan, ko Sitri.  
\v 23 Ez…® Aron Eliseban iti, an Aminadap…®n guivim, egha Nason…®n buaramizim. Egha an a bagha Nadap, Abihu, Eleasar, ko Itamar bate.  
\v 24 Ez…® Kora otarir 3pla iti, Asir, Elkana, ko Abiasap. Me Koran ik…®zim…®n inaziba.  
\v 25 Ez…® Eleasar, Aron…®n otarim, a Putiel…®n guivim…®n itima, an a bagha Finias bate. Gumazir kaba bar, me Livain anabam…®n ik…®zibar dapaniba, me vaghvagha uan ik…®zibar amodogh…®n, me men ziaba osiri.  
\v 26 Ez…® Aron ko Moses aningra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua Israelian anababa bar, dar ik…®ziba vaghvagh me inigh, egh Isip…®n azenan mang…®.‚Äù  
\v 27 Ez…® gumazir kamningra, Moses ko Aron, aning Israelian amamangat…®ght…® me f…®righ…®reghasa Isip…®n atrivim m…®keme. 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akam isa Moses ko Aron gan…®di 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Moses Isip…®n kantrin itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei,  
\v 29 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. Ez…®, akar k…® n…® m…®geiba, n…® bar dar gun Isip…®n atrivim m…®k…®m.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Ez…® Moses a ikara, ‚ÄúN…® fo, nan m…®zem na basemez…®, k…® deragha bizibav geir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n atrivim manmagh…®n na baragham?‚Äù 
\c 7  
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® n…® damight…®, n…® atrivim…®n damazim…®n God…®n m…®n otogham. Eght…® n…®n avebam Aron God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n m…®n otogh…®va, n…®n akaba is…® dar gun atrivim m…®k…®mam.  
\v 2 Eght…® akar gavgavir k…® n…® m…®geiba, n…® bar dar gun Aron m…®kemegh. Eght…® a kamagh…®n atrivim m…®k…®m suam, a Israelia ateght…®, me an kantri ategham.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt Aposel 7:36\x*Eght…® k…® atrivim…®n navim damight…®, a gavgavigham. Guizbang…®ra, k…® Isip…®n kantrin mirakelba ko d…®gavir kuram gamir arazarazir av…®ribar amut…® da otivam,  
\v 4 eght…® atrivim dar gan, egh n…®n akam baraghan kogham. Egh k…® uan gavgavim…®n Isipia ivezir bar kuram me dan…®ngam. Egh nan gumazamiziba Israelia, men anababa bar, k…® me inigh Isip…®n kantrin azenan mangam.  
\v 5 K…® uan gavgavim…®n Isipia ivezir kuram me danigh, egh Israelia inigh Isip…®n kantrin azenan mangam, eght…® dughiar kam…®n Isipia fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Egha Moses ko Aron, Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar gavgavim aning m…®kemez…® mogh…®ram ami.  
\v 7 Dughiar aning atrivim ko m…®kemezir kam, Moses 80plan azeniba iti, ez…® Aron 83plan azeniba iti. 
\s1 Aron…®n asadivir aghorim 
\p  
\v 8-9 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh Moses ko Aron m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim kamagh…®n guan azaragham, gua d…®gavir kuram gamir arazitabar amu, eght…® n…® Aron kamagh a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòN…® uan asadivir aghorim is…® atrivim…®n damazim…®n anekunigh.‚Äô Egh a kamagh…®n damight…®, asadivir aghorim kuruzim…®n otogham.‚Äù  
\v 10 Egha Moses ko Aron atrivim…®n bighan ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akar gavgavim m…®kemez…® mogh…®ram ami. Egha Aron uan asadivir aghorim atrivim ko an ingangarir gumazibar damazim…®n anekuniz…®, a kuruzim…®n oto.  
\v 11 Ez…® atrivim uan fofozir gumaziba ko imezibagh amir gumazibar diaz…® me ize. Isipian imezibagh amir gumazir kaba, uan mogomer akavsiaba inigha uaghan kamagh…®ra dagh ami.  
\v 12 Egha me vaghvagha uan asadivir aghoriba akurima, da kuruzibar otifi. Ez…® Aron…®n asadivir aghorim iza menaba tuvareme.  
\v 13 Ez…® atrivim bizir kam…®n ganigha an navim gavgafi. Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, atrivim Moses ko Aron baraghizir puvat…®. 
\ms1 Arazir kuraba Isipia batifi 
\s1 Faragha zuir arazir kuram, d…®paba ghuzim…®n otifi 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim…®n navim bar gavgaviz…®, a gumazamiziba ateght…® me mangan aghua.  
\v 15 A gurum m…®zaraghara Nail…®n Fanem…®n mang…®t…®, n…® mang…® a batogh. N…® uan asadivir aghorir kuruzim…®n otozim, uan dafarim…®n an suiragh mang…® d…®par m…®riam…®n a m…®zuam.  
\v 16 Egh n…® kamagh…®n atrivim m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, Hibruian God, n…® m…®k…®masa na amadagha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan gumazamizibar amamangat…®ght…®, me nan ziam f…®s…®, gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® n…® an akam baraghizir puvat…®gha iza dat…®r…®k…®n.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 7:17 \xt Akar Mogomem 16:4\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bizir k…® damuamibar ganigh fogh suam, k…®rara Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù N…® gan, k…® uan dafarim…®n suirazir asadivir aghorir kam…®n d…®pam m…®sueght…®, d…®paba bar ragh ghuzim…®n otogham.  
\v 18 Eght…® osiriba bar ar…®m…®ghireght…®, Nail…®n Fanem kurigh m…®ghuaght…®, Isipia an d…®pamra aman iburagham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses uam a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Aron m…®kemeght…®, a uan asadivir aghorim is…®, uan agharim amadagh Isip…®n d…®pabar akaghkagh, faneba, daghuriba, ko d…®par akareba, mozir d…®paba dagh is…®n akakaght…®, d…®paba bar ghuzimram otogham. Egh Isip…®n nguazim bar ghuzimra ik…®va, uaghan iter itariba ko dag…®ar m…®neba sara izevegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® Moses ko Aron Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akar gavgavim m…®kemez…® mogh…®ram ami. Egha aning ghua atrivim ko an ingangarir gumazibar damazim…®n, Aron uan asadivir aghorim fegha, Nail…®n Fanem m…®soke. Ez…® d…®paba bar ragha ghuzim…®n otifi.  
\v 21 Ez…® osirir d…®pam…®n itiba bar ariaghirez…®, d…®pam puv…®ra mughuasi. Ez…® Isipian gumazamiziba an d…®patam raman ibura. Ez…® ghuzim bar Isip…®n danganibar iti.  
\v 22 Ez…® atrivim…®n imezibagh amir gumaziba, uan mogomer akavsiaba inigha uaghan kamagh…®ra dagh ami. Ez…® atrivim…®n navim bar gavgafi. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, atrivim Moses ko Aron baraghan aghua.  
\v 23 Egha atrivim bizir kam m…®gh…®gha a g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®gha, ragha uamategha uan d…®penir ekiam…®n aven ghu.  
\v 24 Ez…® Isipia Nail…®n Fanem…®n d…®pam raman ibura, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me Nail…®n Faner m…®riam…®n d…®pabara amasa mozibagh tui. 
\p  
\v 25 Ikiav…®ra Itir God d…®pam m…®soghez…®ma, d…®pam ikuvigha ikia ghua 7plan arueba g…®fa. 
\c 8  
\s1 M…®tiviba otifi 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® atrivim m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, ‚ÄúNan gumazamiziba ateght…® me mang…®, egh nan ziam fam.‚Äù  
\v 2 Egh n…® aghuaght…®, k…® paz…® n…® damut…® m…®tiviba n…®n kantrin nguazim bar anevaragham.  
\v 3 Eght…® Nail…®n Fanem m…®tiviba a giz…®vagh, egh anetegh mang…®, n…®n d…®penir ekiam…®n mangam. Egh n…® akuir m…®siam ko, n…®n dakozim ko, n…®n ingangarir gumazibar d…®peniba ko, n…®n gumazamizibar d…®peniba ko, n…®n bretba tuer danganiba ko, bretbar ingarir m…®neba, m…®tiviba bar dar mangam.  
\v 4 Egh da uari akun…®va, n…® ko n…®n gumazamiziba, ko n…®n ingangarir gumaziba, da bar ian ghuavanangam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Aron m…®kemeght…®, a uan agharir asadivir aghorim…®n suirazim amadagh. Egh Isip…®n Faneba ko daghuriba ko d…®par akarebagh is…®n a ghufegh, m…®tivibar amight…®, da d…®pam ategh anang Isip…®n nguazim bar anevaragh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Aron uan agharim isa anemadagha d…®pabagh is…®n a ghufez…®, m…®tiviba azenan iza nguazim giz…®fa.  
\v 7 Ez…® imezibagh amir gumaziba uan mogomer akavsiaba inigha uaghan kamagh…®ra dagh amiz…®, m…®tiviba nguazim…®n otifi. 
\p  
\v 8 Egha atrivim Moses ko Aron…®n d…®agha aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemeght…®, a m…®tiviba e dama da batokegh. Eght…® k…® n…®n gumazamiziba ateght…®, me mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofa damuam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Moses a ikara, ‚ÄúK…® n…® bagha God ko m…®k…®masa bar akonge. N…® dughiatam ginabaght…®, k…® n…® ko n…®n ingangarir gumaziba, ko n…®n gumazamiziba, ia bagh God ko m…®k…®mam. Eght…® m…®tiviba ia ategh, tam ua ikian kogham. Da Nail…®n Fanemra ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® atrivim ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® gurum…®n na bagh God ko m…®k…®mam.‚Äù Ez…® Moses a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan azaraz…® mogh…®n, k…® damuam. Eght…® n…® fogh suam, god…®n tam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God…®n m…®n itir puvat…®.  
\v 11 Eght…® n…® uab…®, ko n…®n d…®peniba, n…®n ingangarir gumaziba, ko n…®n gumazamiziba, m…®tiviba bar ia ategh mang…® Nail…®n Fanemra ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Egha Moses ko Aron atrivim ategha ghugha, Moses pamten Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, a m…®tivir a faragha atrivim bagha amadaziba, a da batuegham.  
\v 13 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses an azaraz…® mogh…®n ami, ez…® m…®tivir d…®penibar itiba, ko m…®tivir d…®penir d…®vazibar aven itiba, ko m…®tivir azenibar itiba, da bar tintinibar ariaghire.  
\v 14 Ez…® Isip…®n gumazamiziba dar kuaba akuvagha pozir av…®ribav k…®ni. Ez…® da kurima, dar mughuriam Isip…®n nguazim bar anevara.  
\v 15 Ez…® atrivim gari, m…®tiviba ariaghirez…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, an navim ua gavgaviz…®, a Moses ko Aron baraghan aghua. 
\s1 Itiba otifi 
\p  
\v 16 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Aron m…®kemeght…®, a uan asadivir aghorim is…® nguazim m…®sueght…®, Isip…®n nguazim…®n itir m…®neziba bar ragh itibar otifigh.‚Äù  
\v 17 Egha aning kamagh…®n amigha, Aron uan asadivir aghorim…®n nguazim m…®soghez…®, Isip…®n itir nguazir m…®neziba bar, ragha itibar otivigha, gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba avara.  
\v 18 Ez…® imezibagh amir gumaziba uaghan uan mogomer akavsiaba inigha, itibar amight…® da otivasa, ez…® men imeziba ingarir puvat…®. Ez…® itiba bar danganibar ikia, gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba avara. 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 8:19 \xt Luk 11:20\x*Ez…® imezibagh amir gumaziba, atrivim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod uab…® bizir kam gami!‚Äù Ez…® atrivim…®n navim gavgaviz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, a Moses ko Aron baraghan aghua. 
\s1 Bereziba otifi 
\p  
\v 20 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúGurum m…®zaraghara atrivim d…®pam…®n mang…®t…®, n…® mang…® a batogh a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, N…® nan gumazamiziba ateght…® me mang…®, egh nan ziam fam.  
\v 21 N…® oragh, n…® aghuaght…®, k…® berezir av…®riba amadaght…® da iz…®, n…® uab…® ko, n…®n ingangarir gumaziba, n…®n gumazamiziba ko, ian d…®peniba bar ia bagh izam. Egh Isip…®n d…®peniba bar bereziba iz…®vaghva, nguazir ia apiaghav itiba bar da avaragham.  
\v 22 Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, k…® Gosen…®n Distrigh…®n ganam, egh aneteght…®, berezitam an ikian kogham. Distrigh…®n kam, nan gumazamiziba an iti. K…® kamagh…®n damight…® n…® fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® nguazir kam…®n ingara iti.  
\v 23 Egh k…® uan gumazamiziba ko n…®n gumazamiziba tuiragh, egh uan gumazamizibar akurvagh, n…®n gumazamizibar akurvaghan kogham. N…® gan, gurumzaraghan arazir kam otivam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù  
\v 24 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God arazir kam gami. Egha berezir av…®rim amadaz…®, da atrivim…®n d…®penir ekiam ko, an ingangarir gumazibar d…®penibagh iz…®fa. Egha Isip…®n nguazim, bereziba bar anevaraz…®, a bar ikufi. 
\p  
\v 25 Egha atrivim Moses ko Aron…®n d…®agha aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, kantrin kam…®n averiamra, ofa is…® uan God dan…®ng.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúE kantrin kam…®n aven, uan God…®n ofa damight…®, a deraghan kogham. Guizbang…®ra, e as…®zir Isipia ofa gamir puvat…®ziba, e da is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God en God…®n ofa damight…®, me as…®zir kabar ganigh naviba en ikuvigh, en atar…®va, egh dag…®aba e ginivight…®, e ar…®m…®ghiregham. Kamagh…®n, e kagh ofa damuan kogham.  
\v 27 Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, akar gavgavim e m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, e aruer 3plan mang…® gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…® ofa damuam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® atrivim ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ia ateght…®, ia mang…® gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian God…®n ofa damu, egh bar saghon mangan kogham. Aria, gua na bagh God ko m…®k…®m.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® n…® ategh mang…®, dughiar kamra k…® n…® bagh Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®kemeght…®, gurum…®n bereziba mang…®, n…® ko n…®n ingangarir gumaziba ko n…®n gumazamiziba ategham. N…® orakigh, n…® ua e gifaran mark…®, egh kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogh suam, en gumazamiziba mang…® uan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damuan kogham. Bar mark…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 30 Egha Moses atrivim ategha ghugha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei,  
\v 31 ez…® Moses an azaraz…® mogh…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ami. Ez…® bereziba atrivim…®n ingangarir gumaziba ko an gumazamiziba, bar me ategha ghuez…®, tam ua bar itir puvat…®.  
\v 32 Ez…® dughiar kam atrivim…®n navim ua gavgaviz…®, a gumazamiziba ateght…® me mangan an aghua. 
\c 9  
\s1 As…®ziba ariaghire 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…®va atrivim kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, a Hibruian God, a ghaze: N…® nan gumazamiziba ateght…® me mang…® nan ziam fam.  
\v 2-3 Egh n…® men anogoregh ua me amangan aghuaght…®, k…® paz…® n…® damuva, ar…®mariar kuram n…®n as…®zibar amadagham. Eght…® n…®n hoziaba, donkiba, kamelba, bulmakauba, sipsipba, ko memeba a inigham.  
\v 4 K…®rara Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Israelian as…®ziba ko Isipian as…®ziba tuiraght…® Israelian as…®zitam aremeghan kogham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God dughiam d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® gurum…®n arazir kam damuam.‚Äù  
\v 6 Ez…® am…®nim tiraz…®ma, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami, ez…® Isipian as…®ziba ariaghirez…®, Israelian as…®zitam aremezir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® atrivim uan gumazir maba amadagha men azara, ‚ÄúIsraelian as…®ziba deragha iti, o puvat…®?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® gumazir kaba uamategha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAre, da bar deraghv…®ra iti. Tam aremezir puvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® an navim ua gavgaviz…®, a gumazamiziba ateght…® me mangan an aghua. 
\s1 Okaba Isipian m…®karzibar otifi 
\p  
\v 8 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses ko Aron m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGua brighba tuer d…®penim…®n mang…®, egh uan dafarimning…®n averenir taba inigh…®va, atrivim…®n bighan mang…®va, Moses atrivim…®n damazim…®n averenir kaba akunight…®, da p…®n mavanang.  
\v 9 Egh averenir kaba iregh m…®nezir muziaribar otivigh m…®gh…® Isip…®n nguazim bar anevaragham. Egh da gumazamiziba ko as…®zibagh ireght…®, okaba men m…®karzibar otivigh b…®ghiregh duar ekiabar otivigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 9:10 \xt Akar Mogomem 16:2\x*Egha aning avereniba inigha ghua atrivim…®n damazim…®n tugha, Moses p…®n avereniba kuni. Ez…® avereniba okabagh amiz…®, da otivigha, b…®aghirez…® duar ekiaba gumazamiziba ko as…®zibar otifi.  
\v 11 Ez…® Isipian gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra, okaba me batifi, ez…® imezibagh amir gumaziba uakan. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, me Moses…®n damazim…®n izan ibura.  
