\v 19 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® gumazamiziba m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim me m…®k…®m suam, me uan bulmakauba ko bizir azenan itiba inigh d…®penibar aven dar ar…®gh. Eght…® k…® amozir of…®zir ekiar dag…®abar m…®n gariba amight…®, da ir…®va, gumazamiziba ko as…®zir azenan ikiav…®ra itibagh ir…®t…®, da ar…®m…®ghiram.‚Äù ‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
