\v 34 Ez…® atrivim garima arariba ko amozir of…®zir ekiar dag…®abar m…®n gariba g…®fa. Ez…® a uan ingangarir gumaziba ko, men naviba gavgaviz…®, me uam arazir kuram gami.  
