\c 10  
\s1 Odeziba otifi 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® atrivim…®n gan. K…® kamaghsua ifonge, k…® ua d…®gavir kuram gamir arazaraziba Isipian tong…®n dar amuam. Kamagh…®n k…® atrivim ko an ingangarir gumaziba, me gamiz…®ma, men naviba gavgafi.  
\v 2 K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, ia g…®n uan boriba ko igiar boriba, me m…®k…®m suam, k…® d…®gavir kuram gamir arazarazir kabagh amigha, tuavir kam…®n k…® Isipia gamiz…®ma, me bar onganigha aghums…®ki. K…® kamagh…®n damight…®, ia bar fogh suam, k…® uab…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Egha Moses ko Aron atrivim…®n bighan ghugha, a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a Hibruian God, a ghaze, ‚ÄòDughiar ruarim…®n iza dat…®r…®k…®n, n…® nan akam batoke. N…® uab…® ab…®ragh nan apengan izan aghua, a? N…® nan gumazamizibar amamangat…®ght…® me mang…®, nan ziam fam.  
\v 4 N…® men amamangar…®ghan aghuaght…®, gurumzaraghan k…® odeziba amadaght…®, da n…®n kantri giz…®vagham.  
\v 5 Egh da bar av…®rasemegh, bar nguazim avaraght…®, n…® nguazim…®n ganan kogham. Da bizir, amozir of…®zir ekiar dag…®abar m…®n gariba, as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®ziba bar da amegham. Me dagheba ko temer ian azenibar itiba sara, bar dar am…® da g…®vagham.  
\v 6 Egh da n…®n d…®penir ekiaba ko n…®n ingangarir gumazibar d…®peniba ko n…®n gumazamizibar d…®peniba bar dagh iz…®vagham. N…®n afeziaba ko inaziba, bizir kurar katam, fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, an ganizir puvat…®, bizir kam bar ikuvigham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù Egha Moses atrivim m…®kemegha ua ragha azenan ghu. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® atrivim…®n ingangarir gumaziba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar ruarim…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n otogha, n…® ua manmagh…®n dughiaba gumazir kam ateght…® an e gifar…®va os…®mt…®ziba e dan…®ngam a? N…® Israelian gumazamiziba ateght…® me mang…®, egh uan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fam. N…® ti gara fos ti? Isip bar ikufi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® gumazir maba ghua ua Moses ko Aron inigha atrivim bagha ize. Ez…® an aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian God, an ziam f…®. K…® foghasa, terara mangam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Moses a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúE bar mangam, en boriba ko en gumazamizir ghuriba, en otariba ko guiviba, en sipsipba bar, memeba bar, ko bulmakauba bar. Guizbang…®ra, e isar ekiam damuva, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® atrivim, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam d…®bora akar gavgavim pamtem…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ia ateght…® ia uan amiziba ko boriba inigh mangan kogham! Bar puvat…®gham! K…® kamagh…®n fo, ia arazir kuram…®n e damuasa.  
\v 11 Bar puvat…®gham! Gumazibara mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fam. Ia guizbang…®ra kamaghsua ifonge.‚Äù Atrivim kamagh…®n m…®kemez…®, an ingangarir gumaziba aning batoke. 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan dafarim ghufegh Isip…®n nguazim gis…®n anemadaght…®, odeziba iz…®. Egh da iz…®va, bizir amozir of…®zir ekiar dag…®abar m…®n gariba m…®soghezir puvat…®ziba, odeziba iz…® bar dar amegham.‚Äù  
\v 13 Egha Moses uan asadivir aghorim ghufegha Isip…®n kantri gis…®n anemada. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God am…®nim gamiz…®ma, an aruem anadi nagh…®n ikegha iza, nguazim gis…®n vav…®ra ikia ghua aruem ko d…®magarim, ghua g…®fa. Ez…® am…®nim tiraz…®ma, me garima, odeziba otivigha g…®fa.  
\v 14 Egha odeziba bar av…®rasemegha iza Isip…®n danganiba bar da avara. Ez…® fom…®ra Isipia kamagh…®n odezir av…®rir okoruar kamagh…®n garir tabar ganizir puvat…®, egh me g…®n ua dar ganighan kogham.  
\v 15 Odeziba nguazim bar anevaraz…®, nguazim bar p…®ghiz…®, da amozir dag…®aba faragha irava as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®zir biziba ko, azenibar otivir biziba ko iter ov…®ziba, odeziba bar da ame. Ez…® temer dafarir gariba ko graziba ua Isip…®n kantri itir puvat…®. Da bar g…®fa. 
