\v 16 Ez…® atrivim zuam…®ra Moses ko Aron bagha akam amadaz…®, aning izez…®, an aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® arazir kuram Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God a gami, egha uaghan gua gami.  
\v 17 K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, gua dughiar kamra ua nan arazir kuram g…®n amadagh. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, guan God, gua a ko m…®kemeght…®, a bizir kurar na gas…®ghas…®ghasava amir kam na dama a inigh.‚Äù  
