\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ua ivezir kurar abuananam Isipian atrivim ko an gumazamizibar an…®ngam. Eght…® ivezir kurar kam otoght…®, a ia amadaght…® ia mangam. Egh a navir am…®rizim sara ian amamat…®ghan kogham. Puvat…®gham. A zuam…®ra navir kuram sara nguibar kam…®n ia batueght…® ia bar mangam.  
\v 2 N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Israelian gumazamizibav kemeght…®, men gumaziba ko amiziba vaghvagh mang…®, Isip…®n men borogh…®n tibar bighan mang…®, men azangs…®ght…®, me kuritir bizir aghuir me gol ko, silvan ingariziba ko, bizir gol…®n ingarizir igharaziba sara me dan…®ng.‚Äù 
