\v 5 \x - \xo 11:5 \xt Onger Akaba 78:51; 105:36; 136:10\x*Eght…® Isipian otarir ivariaba vaghvagh ar…®m…®ghiram. Atrivim, n…®n otarir ivariar n…®n danganim inigh atrivim ikiamim, faragha aremegham. Eght…® otarir ivariaba bar ar…®ghir…® mang…®, ingangarir amizir k…®nir wit m…®rm…®riba, men otarir ivariaba uaghan ar…®ghiram. Eght…® bulmakaun apurir faragha otoziba, uaghan bar ar…®ghiram. Isipian otarir ivariaba bar aremegham.  
\v 6 Eght…® Isipian gumazamiziba bar naviba osemegh, pamten azi ararer ekiam damuam. Fom…®ra ararer ekiar kamagh garitam Isip…®n otozir puvat…®, egh tam g…®n uam kamagh otivan kogham.  
