\p  
\v 9 Ikiav…®ra Itir God faragha kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim n…®n akam bareghan kogham. Kamagh…®n, k…® ua Isip…®n d…®gavir kuram gamir arazir av…®ritabar amuam.‚Äù 
