\v 1 \x - \xo 12:1-13 \xt Ofa Gami 23:5; D…®boboniba 9:1-5; 28:16; God…®n Araziba 16:1-2\x*Ez…® Moses ko Aron Isip…®n kantrin ikiav…®ra itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n aning m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúIak…®nir kam, a ian azenibar faragha zuir iak…®nim…®n ikiam.  
\v 3 N…® Israelian gumazamiziba kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, iak…®nir kam…®n aruer namba 10, gumazamiziba bar vaghvagh uan adarazi bagh sipsip…®n igiatam ko memen igiatam, am…®sefegh.  
\v 4 Egh d…®penir vam…®ran itir adarasi av…®rasemeghan kogh…®va, me uarir borogh…®n itir daraziv m…®kemeght…®, me iz…® as…®zir kam tuiragh uari dan…®ng anerem…®. Me deraghv…®ra n…®ghnigh, as…®zir kam deragh gumaziba ko, amiziba ko, boribar tuiraght…®, me as…®zir tuzir kam ag…®vagham.  
\v 5 Egh n…® ua bagh vaghvagh sipsip…®n apuritam o memen apuritam am…®seveght…®, an azenir vam…®ra ik…®t…®, duatam an m…®karzim…®n ikian mark…®.  
\v 6 Egh me as…®zir kaba uari bagh deraghv…®ra dar gan mang…® iak…®nir kam…®n aruer 14…®n otogh. Eght…® dughiar kamra, an guarat…®zim…®n, Israelian gumazamiziba bar uan as…®zir kabav sueght…®, da ar…®ghiregh.  
\v 7 Egh me as…®zim…®n ghuzitaba inigh, uan d…®penim…®n tiar akabar m…®riabagh asezir tememning daghuigh, d…®penir kam…®n aven me ik…® as…®zibar amam. Egh uaghan tiar akam gis…®n itir ter ighuvim aghefegh.  
\v 8 Egh d…®magarir kam…®n me sipsip o memen tuzim avim…®n a tuagh, egh ia as…®zir tuzir kam yis puvat…®zir bret ko zuravarir m…®sozim sara anerem…®.  
\v 9 Egh ia as…®zir tuzir angamt…®zim, ko tuzir m…®nem…®n avighizitam aman mark…®. Ia avim…®n dar dapaniba, ko sueba ko dafariba, ko navir averim…®n itir biziba sara, ia bar da tuegh, dar am…®.  
\v 10 Egh ia as…®zir otevitaba ateght…® da ik…® am…®mzaraghan ikian mark…®. Da ik…®t…® am…®nim tiraght…®, ia dar naba tueght…® da bar isi m…®gh…®righ.  
\v 11 Egh ia as…®zir kabar am…®s…® kamagh…®n damu. Ia iniba ikegh dagarir asuabar aghuigh, asadivir aghoribar suigh zuam…®ra dar am…®. Isar ekiar kam, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam. 
\p  
\v 12 ‚ÄúEght…® d…®magarir kamra, k…® Isip…®n danganiba bar dar mang…®, gumazamizibar otarir ivariaba ko as…®zibar apurir ivariaba, k…® dav soght…® me bar ar…®m…®ghiregham. Eght…® Isip…®n aseba bar, k…® ivezir kuraba me dan…®ngam. Guizbang…®ra, k…® uab…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.  
\v 13 Ghuzir ia uan d…®peniba aghevezir kaba, da ababanim…®n m…®n ikiam. Eght…® k…® Isipian gumazamiziba paz…® me damuva ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam. K…® ghuzim…®n ganigh, ian d…®penibagh itagham. Egh k…® ia ateght…®, ivezir kurar kam ia batoghan kogham. Eght…® ia deraghv…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 12:14-20 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:15; 34:18; Ofa Gami 23:6-8; D…®boboniba 28:17-25; God…®n Araziba 16:3-8\x*‚ÄúEght…® ia dughiar kam g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra ik…®t…®, a ian dughiar ekiam…®n m…®n ikiam. K…® dughiar kam ginabaght…®, a nan ziam feir isar ekiam…®n m…®n ikiam. Eght…® ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God amir arazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gham. Eght…® ian g…®n otivamin adarasi, bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemezim…®n g…®n mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh isar kam damuv…®ra ik…®t…®, a ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam 
\p  
\v 15 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa faragh…®v…®ra uan d…®penibar yisba batokegh. Egh ia 7plan dughiabar, yis puvat…®zir bret am…®. Gumazitam 7plan dughiar kabar aven, dar dughiatam yis itir bret ameght…®, ia Israelian gumazamizibar tong…®n a batokegh.  
\v 16 Egh faragha zuir dughiam ko namba 7…®n dughiam, ia uari akuvagh God…®n ziam fer arazim damu. Egh ia ingangarir igharazibar amuan mark…®. Ia uari bagh daghebara tu.  
\v 17 Ez…® 7plan dughiabar faragha zuir dughiamra, k…® ian anababa Isip…®n kantrin me inigha azenan ghu. Ez…® azeniba bar dughiar ekiar kam…®n, kar Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam, dughiar kam, a bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®ghamin dughiam…®n m…®n ikiam. Eght…® ian g…®n otivamin adarasi, bizir a damuasa ia m…®kemezim…®n g…®n mang…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh isar kam damuv…®ra ik…®t…®, a ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúEgh ia iak…®nir faragha zuiba bar, dar dughiar 14…®n guarat…®zibar, yis puvat…®zir bret am…® mang…®, egh dughiar 21…®n otogh.  
\v 19 Egh 7plan dughiar kabar aven, yis ian d…®penibar ikian mark…®. Eght…® ian gumazitam, o kantrin igharazim…®n gumazir ia ko ititam, a yis itir bret ameght…®, ia Israelian gumazamizibar tong…®n a batokegh.  
\v 20 Ia oragh. Ia tintinim…®n managh iti, ia yis itir bret raman mark…®. Ia yis puvat…®zir bret am…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Me as…®zibav sogha isam gamua God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®si 
\p  
\v 21 Egha Moses Israelian gumazir dapanibar diaz…® me izez…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa vaghvagh mang…® sipsip…®n igiatam o memen igiatam am…®sefegh, uan adarazi bagh dav suegh, God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam damuam.  
\v 22 Egh ia ghuzim itarir ekiam gingegh, hisop…®n ter aguar muziaritam inigh, a is…® ghuzim itir itarir ekiam darugh. Egh ghuzir muziarim inigh uan d…®penibar tiar akabar m…®riam…®n tughav itir tememning daghuigh, egh tiar akam gis…®n itir ter ighuvim aghefegh. Egh ia bar d…®penim…®n aven ik…®, tav azenan mangan mark…® mang…®, m…®zarazim…®n otogh.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 12:23 \xt Hibru 11:28\x*G…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isipian otarir ivariabav sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghir…®s…® Isip…®n danganiba bar dar mangam. A ian tiar akabar ghuzim…®n ganigh, ia ateght…® gumazibagh as…®ghas…®ghamin ensel aven mang…® ian otarir ivariabav sueght…®, me ar…®m…®ghireghan kogham. 
\p  
\v 24 ‚ÄúEght…® ia uan boriba ko, bizir a damuasa e m…®kemeziba zurara azenibar dar amuv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 25 Ia mang…® nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia dan…®ngasa m…®kemegha, akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamizim…®n dapiagh…®va, God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®gh…®va isar kam damu.  
\v 26 Eght…® g…®n ian boriba kamagh…®n ian azangs…®gham, ‚ÄòKar manmagh…®n amizir isar kam?‚Äô  
\v 27 Eght…® ia kamagh…®n me m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIsar kam, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamua, God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®si. A fom…®ra Isipian otarir ivariabav soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha a Israelia en d…®peniba gitav…®ragha, en otarir ivariaba ataghiz…® me derav…®ra iti. Ez…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kam g…®n…®ghn…®si.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù Ez…® gumazamiziba akar kam baregha dapaniba avigha God…®n ziam fe.  
\v 28 Egha me g…®n d…®kavigha ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God damuasa Moses ko Aron m…®kemezir biziba, me dagh ami. 
\s1 Otarir ivariaba ariaghire 
\p  
\v 29 \x - \xo 12:29 \xt Ua Me Ini 4:22-23\x*Ez…® d…®magarir ar…®zim…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isipian otarir ivariabav suaghar…®si. A faragha atrivim…®n otarir ivariam m…®suegha, ghua otarir ivariar igharazibav sogha ghuav…®ra ikia ghua kalabuziar gumazibar, otarir ivariaba sara m…®soke. Egha uaghan bulmakaubar apurir ivariabav soke.  
\v 30 Ez…® d…®magarir kamra, atrivim ko, an ingangarir gumaziba, ko Isipia bar d…®kavigha garima, men otarir ivariaba ariaghiregha g…®fa. Men d…®peniba bar mogh…®ra vaghvagha, men otarir ivariaba ariaghire. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Isip…®n danganiba bar, gumazamiziba azirakar ekiam gami.  
\v 31 Ez…® d…®magarir kamra atrivim Moses ko Aron…®n diagha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bar d…®kavigh mang…®. Gua ko Israelian gumazamiziba bar, ia zuam…®ra mang…®, nan gumazamizibagh itagh. Ia mang…®, ia nan azaraz…® mogh…®n, mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam f…®.  
\v 32 Egh ia uan sipsipba, memeba, bulmakauba inigh, ia nan azaraz…® mogh…®n, da inigh bar Isip ategh mang…®. Egh na bagh God ko m…®k…®mt…®, a deragh na damu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 33 Ez…® Isipia Israelian gumazamizibar av…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa zuam…®ram Isip ategh mang…®. Ia zuam…®ra e gitaghan koght…®, e bar ar…®m…®ghiregham.‚Äù  
\v 34 Ez…® Israelia plauan me t…®ghar yis sara vereghamiba, da inigha, itarir ekiabagh ar…®ki. Egha me itarir ekiaba inibar da noegha, d…®p…®zibar da atera zui.  
\v 35 \x - \xo 12:35-36 \xt Ua Me Ini 3:21-22\x*Israelia Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, me Isipia bagha ghua kuritir bizir aghuir me gol ko, silvan ingariziba ko, korotiaba bagha uaghan men azai.  
\v 36 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Isipian damazim…®n ziar ekiam Israelia gan…®di. Ez…® Isipia bizir Israelia ifongeziba me gan…®di. Ez…® tuavir kam…®n Israelia, Isipian bizir aghuiba, puram ada inigha ghue. 
\s1 Israelia d…®kavigha ghua  // Isip…®n kantrin azenan ghue 
\p  
\v 37 Israelian gumazamiziba d…®kavigha Rameses…®n nguibam ategha ghua nguibar ekiam Sukot…®n danganim…®n zui. Gumazir 600,000plan, uan suebar arua zuir kaba, me gumazibara. Me amiziba ko boriba mengezir puvat…®.  
\v 38 Ez…® gumazamizir igharazir av…®rir maba, ko bulmakauba, sipsipba ko memen av…®rir maba uaghan me ko zui.  
\v 39 Me tuavim…®n ghua Isip…®n inizir plaua yis puvat…®zim…®n bret tue. Isipian gumaziba men av…®ghav…®ra iti, me dagheba ak…®ramin dughiaba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, me yis isa plaua gat…®zir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 40 \x - \xo 12:40 \xt Jenesis 15:13; Galesia 3:17\x*Israelia 430plan azenibar Isip…®n kantrin ike.  
\v 41 Ez…® aruer kamra, men 430plan azenim…®n aruer abuananam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamiziba Isip ategha azenan zui.  
\v 42 Ez…® d…®magarir kamra Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia deraghv…®ra men gara, egha Isip…®n kantrin me inigha azenan ize. Egh zurara azenir g…®n izamibar, men g…®n otivighamin adarasi, me d…®magarir kamra angam…®ra ik…® gan…®va, Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®n…®ghn…®gh…®va, an ziam fam. 
\s1 God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam…®n isam…®n g…®n mangamin arazibar,  // akar gavgaviba Israelia gan…®ngi 
\p  
\v 43 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses ko Aron m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam…®n isam…®n arazibagh n…®ghn…®gh kamagh…®n damu. Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, isar kam…®n daghetamra aman mark…®.  
\v 44-45 Eght…® gumazir dughiar otevim…®n ia ko itiba, ko gumazir dag…®aba bagha ingara itiba, me isar kam…®n daghetam aman kogham. Ez…® gumazir ia ivezez…® me ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n itima, ia men m…®karzir mogomebar inibar aghore, merara uaghan ia ko isar kam…®n daghetam amam. 
\p  
\v 46 \x - \xo 12:46 \xt D…®boboniba 9:12; Jon 19:36\x*‚ÄúEgh gumazamiziba, d…®penir me aven ikia as…®ziba tuezim, me d…®penir kam…®n averara ik…®, egh as…®zir tuzibar am…®. Me daghetaba inigh azenan mangan mark…®. Egh uaghan me as…®zir agharibar am…® dar p…®ran mark…®.  
\v 47 Israelian gumazamiziba bar isar kam…®n aven ik…® dam…®. 
\p  
\v 48 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazir uan m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim atuzir puvat…®zim, daman kogham. Kantri igharazim…®n gumazim iza ian kantrin aven iti, a God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam…®n isam ia ko a damus…®, ia an m…®karzir mogomem…®n inim atugh. Egh uaghan gumazir an ik…®zim…®n itiba sara, men m…®karzir mogomebar iniba aghoregh. Eght…® a ian gumazim…®n m…®n ik…®, ian adarazi ko dam…®.  
\v 49 Ez…® arazir kabara Israelian gumazamiziba, ko gumazir kantrin igharazibar ikegha iza ia ko itiba, uaghara arazir kabar g…®n mang…®.‚Äù  
\v 50 Ez…® Israelia, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses ko Aron m…®kemez…® mogh…®rama ami.  
\v 51 Ez…® dughiar kamra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian anababar aven vaghvagha bar me inigha Isip…®n kantrin azenan ghu. 
\c 13  
\s1 Israelia otarir ivariaba isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®di 
\p  
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 13:1-2 \xt D…®boboniba 3:13; Luk 2:23\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bar uan otarir ivariaba na danight…®, me na baghv…®ra ikiam. Israelia, ian otarir ivariaba, ko as…®zir apurir ivariaba, bar nana.‚Äù 
\s1 Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIa faragha Isip…®n kantrin ikia, ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan gavgavim…®n ia inigha azenan ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia zurara dughiabar, dughiar kam ko an amizir arazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, yis itir bret tam aman mark…®.  
\v 4 Ia Isip ataghizir dughiar kam…®n faragha zuir iak…®nim, an ziam, Abip.\f + \fr 13:4 \ft Israelian iak…®nir kam, ‚ÄúAbip,‚Äù an en iak…®nir kamning…®n otifi, Mas ko Epril.\f* 
\v 5 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian inazir afeziaba ko akam ak…®righa ghaze, a nguazim is…® ia dan…®ngam. Nguazir kam, Kenania, Hitia, Amoria, Hivia ko Jebusia dat…®r…®gh…®n a gapiaghav iti. Nguazir kam a bar deraz…®, biziba an ikiava bar deraghav…®ram aghui. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia inigh nguazir kam…®n mang…®ght…®, g…®n izamin azenibar iak…®nir kamra, ia Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam damuam. 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúEgh ia yis puvat…®zir bret 7plan arueba anem…®, mang…®va namba 7…®n aruem…®n tugh. Eght…® namba 7…®n aruem otoght…®, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam f…®.  
\v 7 Egh 7plan aruer kaba, gumazamiziba yis puvat…®zir bretra dam…®. Egh ia bret…®n yis itim ko yis tam ateght…®, a ian nguibatam…®n aven ikian mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, yis ian kantrin aven ikian kogham.  
\v 8 Eght…® dughiar ekiar kam otoght…®, ia uan otariba kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God Isip…®n kantrin aven e bagha bizir ekiabagh amigha, en adarazi inigha azenan ize. Ez…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n isar ekiam gamua, bizir kaba bar dagh n…®ghn…®si.‚Äô  
\v 9 Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan gavgavim…®n pamtem ingara, e inigha Isip…®n kantrin azenan ize. Eght…® isam…®n arazir kam ian dafariba ko guabar, osizirim…®n m…®n ik…®. Eght…® a ia bagh arazir an amizim…®n ababanim…®n m…®n ik…®. Egh a ia damight…® ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akar gavgavibar gun m…®k…®mam.  
\v 10 Egh azeniba bar, ia isar a damuasa m…®kemezir kam, an dughiamra a damuam.‚Äù 
\s1 Otarir ivariaba 
\p  
\v 11 Egha Moses kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ia inigh Kenanian nguazim…®n mangam. A nguazir kam bagha, faragha ia ko ian ovaviba ko akam ak…®ri. Egh nguazir kam ia dan…®ngam.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 13:12 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:19-20; Luk 2:23\x*A ia danigh g…®vaght…®, ia uan otarir ivariaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngam. Eght…® ian as…®zir apurir ivariaba uaghan, da God…®n anaba.  
\v 13 Ia sipsip…®n nguzir tam is…® ofa damu, egh tuavir kam…®n ia donkin apurir ivariam givezegh ua a iniam. Ia donkin apurir ivariam givezan aghuagh, ia an gurim ap…®righ. Egh ia uan otarir ivariaba vaghvagha ua me givezegh me iniam.  
\v 14 Egh g…®n izamin dughiaba ian otariba kamagh…®n ian azangs…®gh suam, ‚ÄòKar manmagh…®n amizir arazim?‚Äô Eght…® ia kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòE ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n Isip…®n kantrin ingara itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan gavgavim…®n pamten ingara, e inigha azenan ize.  
\v 15 Ez…® faragha Isip…®n atrivim…®n navim gavgaviz…®, an e ateght…® e mangan an aghua. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Isipian otarir ivariaba, ko men as…®zir apurir ivariabav soghez…® da ariaghire. Ez…® e dat…®r…®k…®n as…®zir apurir ivariaba bar da inigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha dar ofa gami. Egha e uan otarir ivariabagh ivezegha ua me ini.‚Äô  
\v 16 Ia arazir kam damuva, Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®n…®ghn…®gh suam, a uan gavgavim…®n Isip…®n kantrin e inigha azenan ize. Eght…® arazir kam, ian dafariba ko guabar osizirim…®n m…®n ik…®. Egh arazir kam ia bagh, ababanim…®n m…®n ik…®va ian n…®ghn…®zibar amut…® da d…®kavam.‚Äù 
\s1 God ghuariar ruarir ekiar mam ko, avir m…®zariar ruarir ekiar mam…®n aven ikia men faragha zui 
\p  
\v 17 Atrivim Israelian gumazamiziba ataghiz…® me zuir dughiam…®n, God kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúIsraelia tuavir otevim…®n mang…® igharaz darazir gant…®, me me m…®soghs…® damut…®, me uan n…®ghn…®zibagh iragh, uamategh Isip…®n mang…®s…® n…®ghn…®gham. Ez…® Israelia kamagh…®n damuan k…® ifongezir puvat…®.‚Äù Kamagh…®n, God tuavir otevim…®n me inigha Filistian kantrin ongarir dadarim…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 18 Ez…® kamagh…®n, God Israelia inigha ghuanaga gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghua Ongarir Aghevim…®n oto. Egha me m…®dorozim gamir biziba inigha da sara zui. 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 13:19 \xt Jenesis 50:25; Josua 24:32\x*Bar fom…®ra, Josep kamagh…®n Israelia m…®keme, ‚ÄúBar g…®n God Isip…®n ua ia inigh ian akurvagham. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n ia nan aghariba inigh da sara mang…®.‚Äù Ez…® Israelia akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamiz…® mogh…®n, Moses Josep…®n aghariba inigha zui. 
\p  
\v 20 Egha Israelia d…®kavigha Sukot…®n danganim ategha ghua Etam…®n nguibam…®n oto, me gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n m…®riam…®n otoghava apia.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 13:21 \xt Ua Me Ini 14:19; 14:24; 33:9; Onger Akaba 78:14; 105:39\x*Egha aruebar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghuariar ruarir ekiam…®n aven ikia, men faragha ghua tuavim men akakasi. Egha d…®magaribar ana avir m…®zariar ruarir ekiam…®n aven ikia, me gis…®rara ikia men faragha ghua angazangarim me gan…®di. Ez…® bizir kam bang…®n, me arueba ko d…®magariba sara arua zui.  
\v 22 Ez…® aruebar zurara ghuariar ruarir ekiar kam men faragha zui, egha d…®magaribar avir m…®zariar ruarir ekiar kam men faragha zui. Aning uan danganimning atagh…®razir puvat…®gha kamagh…®ra iti. 
\c 14  
\s1 Me Ongarir Aghevim ab…®ki 
\p  
\v 1-2 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Israelia m…®kemeght…®, me uamategh mang…® ongarir m…®riam…®n Pihahirot…®n nguibam…®n dapiagh. Nguibar kam, a Mikdol…®n nguibam ko Ongarir Aghevim…®n tizim…®n ikia, Balsefon…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n iti.  
\v 3 Eght…® Isip…®n atrivim men darorim g…®n…®ghn…®gh, kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIsraelia ti onganigha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim puram a garuama. Me danganir kam ategh mangamin tuaviba puvat…®gham.‚Äô  
\v 4 K…® atrivim damight…® an navim gavgavight…®, a ian ag…®ragham. Eght…® k…® a ko an m…®dorozir gumaziba, me d…®kab…®ragh me ab…®ragham. Egh bizir kam bang…®n k…® ziar ekiam iniam. Eght…® Isipia fogh suam, K…®rara, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù Ez…® Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam baregha, uamategha ghua Pihahirot…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n apia. 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® gumazir maba Isip…®n atrivim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIsraelia ara ghue.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® a ko an ingangarir gumazibar n…®ghn…®zibagh iragha ghaze, ‚ÄúManmagh amiz…®, e Israelia ataghiz…® me ghue? Me dat…®r…®gh…®n uam en ingangaribar amuan kogham. Guizbang…®ra, e pazava amigha g…®fa!‚Äù  
\v 6 Egha me m…®kemegha g…®vagha, atrivim uan m…®dorozir karisba ko, m…®dorozir gumaziba ini.  
\v 7 Egha uaghan a 600plan karis…®n m…®dorozim gamir aghuariba, ko Isip…®n m…®dorozir karis…®n igharaziba sara inigha, karisbar garir gumazir dapaniba inigha, me d…®kavigha Israelian g…®n zui.  
\v 8 Israelia fo, me Isipia d…®kab…®nigha me ab…®nigha, bar akongegha zui. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isip…®n atrivim gamiz…®, an navim gavgaviz…®, a zuam…®ra d…®kavigha men g…®nt…®ghasa zui.  
\v 9 Isipian m…®dorozir gumaziba, uan karisba ko bar zui, marazi hoziabagh apiagha zui, ez…® marazi uan suebar ghua, bar Israelian ag…®nt…®gha zui. Egha me bar ghua Israelia apiagha itir danganim…®n otifi. Danganir kam, an Ongarir Aghevim…®n m…®riam…®n ikia, Pihahirot…®n borogh…®n iti, ez…® Balsefon an ak…®rang…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Isip…®n atrivim uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, Israelian borogh…®n zuima, Israelia men api. Egha me bar puv…®ra atiatigha, uarir akurvaghasa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n dei.  
\v 11 Me kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha e inigha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganir kam…®n ize? N…® ghaze, Isip…®n kantrin moziba okoramin danganiba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n e ti ar…®m…®ghirasa, n…® e inigha kagh ize? N…® manmagh…®n e gamua, e inigha Isip ategha azenan ize?  
\v 12 E Isip atagh…®raghasava amir dughiam, e kamagh…®n n…® m…®keme, ‚ÄòArazir kurar kaba e bativam.‚Äô E n…® m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® e ateght…® e Isip…®n ik…®va, ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n ik…®t…® deragham. Puvat…®ght…®, e gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ar…®m…®ghiram.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Moses kamagh…®n me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa atiatingan mark…®, ia tuivigh gavgafigh. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gavgavim…®n ganight…®, a ian akuragh ua ia inian. Ia dat…®r…®k…®n Isipian gari, ia ua men ganan kogham.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 14:14 \xt Ua Me Ini 15:3; God…®n Araziba 1:30; 3:22; Aisaia 30:15\x*Ia orakigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian akurvaghs…® me ko m…®sogham. Ia uari bizitam damuan mark…®. Ia n…®m…®ra ik…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha nan ingarava arav…®ra iti? N…® Israelia m…®kemeght…®, me mang…®.  
\v 16 Eght…® n…® uan asadivir aghorim ghufegh, ongarim gis…®n amadagh. Eght…® ongarim bigh akuar pumuning ir…®ght…®, Israelia nguazir dak…®rt…®zim…®n mang…® vong…®n otifigh.  
\v 17 Eght…® k…® Isipia damight…® men naviba gavgavight…®, me ian g…®n ongarim biaghir…®zir tuavim…®n mangam. Eght…® k…® atrivim ko, an karisba ko, m…®dorozir gumazir hoziabagh apiaziba, ko m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me d…®kab…®ragham. Egh k…® me gamizir arazir kam bagh, ziar ekiam iniam.  
\v 18 K…® Isipia d…®kab…®ragh me ab…®raght…® me fogh suam, K…®rara, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® God…®n ensel…®n zurara Israelian m…®dorozir gumazibar faragha zuim, a s…®vagha ghua men ak…®rang…®n tu. Ez…® ghuariar ruarir ekiar zurara men faragha zuim, a uaghan is…®vagha ghua men ak…®rang…®n tu.  
\v 20 D…®magarir kam…®n, ghuariar ruarir ekiar kam Israelia ko, Isipian t…®zim…®n tughav iti. Ghuariar ruarir kam Isipia itir danganim gamiz…®, a bar m…®tatangi. Egha Israelia itir danganim angazangarim a gan…®ngi.\f + \fr 14:20 \ft Hibru akam vez…®n kam deragha a m…®geir puvat…®.\f* Kamagh…®n, d…®magarir kam…®n Isipia ko Israelia uarir borogh…®n mangan ibura. 
\p  
\v 21 Moses uan agharim ghufegha, ongarim gis…®n anemada. Ez…® d…®magarim…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, am…®nir gavgavim gamiz…®, an aruem anadi nagh…®n oto. Egha d…®magarir kam…®n am…®nim ongarim g…®va ghuavti am…®nim tira. Ez…® ongarim tong…®ra biaghir…®gha, akuar pumuning…®n ir…®gha nguazir dak…®rt…®zim…®n oto.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 14:22 \xt 1 Korin 10:1-2; Hibru 11:29\x*Egha d…®vazimning…®n m…®n vong ko vong…®n akuvagha itima, Israelia aning…®n tong…®n nguazir dak…®rt…®zim…®n ghua vong…®n otifi.  
\v 23 Ez…® Isip…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba Israelian ag…®ragha, men g…®n ghua ongarim…®n tong…®ra ghu. Men hoziaba ko, karisba ko, gumazir hoziabagh apiziba, da bar zui.  
\v 24 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, aviv zariam…®n m…®n ghuariar ruarir kam…®n aven iti. Ez…® am…®nim tiasa amima, a Isipian m…®dorozir gumaziba, men n…®ghn…®zibagh iraz…®ma, me tintinibar n…®ghn…®gha atiatia arasava ami.  
\v 25 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, karisbagh amiz…®, nguazim dar wilbar suighiz…®, da pamten ivemarir puvat…®. Ez…® Isipia uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúIa oragh, E zuam…®rama ar…® mangeka! Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian akuragha e m…®sosi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan agharim ghufegh, ongarim gis…®n anemadaght…®, d…®pam ua iz…® Isipian m…®dorozir gumaziba, ko men karisba ko gumazir hoziabagh apiaziba, bar me avaragh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® Moses agharim ghufegha ongarim gis…®n anemada. Am…®nim tiraz…®ma, ongarim ua iza faragha ikez…® mogh…®n uan danganim…®n iti. Dughiar kamra, Isipia ar…® mangasa amuav…®ra itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, bar me avigha ongarim m…®k…®ni.  
\v 28 Ez…® ongarim uamategha ize. Egha gumazir atrivim…®n hoziabagh apiaziba ko, m…®dorozir gumazir Israelian g…®n ongarir torim…®n ghueziba, bar me avara. Ez…® men tav m…®seveagh…®r…®zir puvat…®.  
\v 29 Ongarim d…®vazim m…®n, vong ko vong…®n akuvagha itima, Israelia nguazir dak…®rt…®zim…®n zui. 
\p  
\v 30 Dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isipian dafarim…®n Israelia, ua men akura. Ez…® Israelia, Isipian kuabar garima, da ongarir dadarim…®n ireghav iti.  
\v 31 Israelian gumazamiziba garima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan gavgavir ekiam…®n pamtem ingara, Isipia d…®kab…®ragha me ab…®ra. Ez…® me bar atiatigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. Egha an ingangarir gumazim Moses, me uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. 
\c 15  
\s1 Moses…®n Onger Akam 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 15:1 \xt Akar Mogomem 15:3\x*Dughiar kam Moses Israelian gumazamiziba ko, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ighiar kam kamagh…®n a bange: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a m…®dorozir ekiam ab…®ra, ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n a bagh onger akam bangam. 
\q2 Guizbang…®ra, a hoziaba ko gumazir hoziabagh is…®n apiaziba me avigha ongarim m…®k…®ni. 
\q2 An apaniba ab…®ra, ez…® an ziam bar p…®n iti! 
\q1  
\v 2 \x - \xo 15:2 \xt Ua Me Ini 3:6; 3:15; Aisaia 12:2\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® na gamiz…®ma, k…® gavgavigha, onger akam bangava an ziam fe. 
\q2 A zurara ua na isi, ez…® k…® an ziam fasa. 
\q1 A nan God, egha nan akurvazim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® an ziar ekiam fasa. 
\q2 Nan afeziam…®n God, k…® an ziar ekiam f…®, a is…® bar p…®n aner…®gh ighiam damuam. 
\q1  
\v 3 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a bar m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavim. 
\q2 Ziar kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kar an ziam. 
\q1  
\v 4 A Isipian m…®dorozir gumaziba ko men karis…®n m…®dorozim gamiba, a me avigha me isa ongarim m…®k…®ni. 
\q2 Ez…® men m…®dorozir gumazir dapaniba, ongarim amegha Ongarir Aghevim…®n aven ariaghire. 
\q1  
\v 5 Ongarim bar me avaraz…®ma, 
\q2 me dag…®abar m…®n ongarir d…®k…®nim giraghue. 
\q1  
\v 6 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n agharir guvim bar gavgavir ekiam iti, 
\q2 n…® uan apaniba d…®karagha bar me m…®rm…®ri. 
\q1  
\v 7 N…® uan gavgavir ekiam…®n uan apaniba ab…®ra, 
\q2 egha n…® uan navir an…®ngazim avim…®n m…®n otogha men isia, mati avim grazir m…®diaribar isi. 
\q1  
\v 8 N…® am…®nir ekiam gamiz…® a d…®kavigha, ongarim gamiz…®ma, a buigha p…®n anabo. 
\q2 Egha vorogh…®ra d…®vazim…®n m…®n tughav iti. Ez…® ongarir apebam…®n itim, bar pamtem…®n ingara gavgafi. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 9 ‚ÄúApaniba ghaze, ‚ÄòE men ag…®nt…®gh men suigham. 
\q2 Egh men bizir aghuariba inigh da tuis…®gh uan adarazir an…®ngam. 
\q2 Egh e bizir manam inis…® e puram a iniam. 
\q2 E sabar m…®sozim asigh, uan gavgavim…®n me gas…®ghas…®gham.‚Äô 
\q1  
\v 10 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® uan am…®nim dughiar vam…®ran a giveraz…®ma, ongarim Isipia avara. 
\q2 Ez…® me dag…®am…®n m…®n ongarir bar puv…®ra ingarim giraghue. 
\q1  
\v 11 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ua god…®n manam ikia n…®n m…®n gavgafi? Tav ua itir puvat…®. 
\q2 N…® atrivir ekiam, egha arazir aghuibaram ami. 
\q2 N…® bar p…®n koz…®, e n…®n atiati. Tina n…®n m…®n iti? Tav ua itir puvat…®. 
\q2 N…®rara d…®gavir kuram gamir arazibagh ami, egha ingangarir ekiabagh ami. 
\q1  
\v 12 N…® uan agharir guvim a ghufegha anemadaz…®, 
\q2 nguazim akam akarigha apaniba tuavareme. 
\q1  
\v 13 N…® bar uan gumazamiziba men apangkuvigha men akuragha me inigha, men faragha ghua me inigha zui. 
\q2 N…® uan gavgavim…®n men darorim…®n faragha ghua, danganir aghuarir n…® uab…® itimra, n…® men akua a bagha zui. 
\q1  
\v 14 Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba arazir n…® amizim baregha, pamten n…®ghava atiati. 
\q2 Ez…® Filistiaba uaghan aguava bar puv…®rama atiati. 
\q1  
\v 15 Idom…®n kantrin faragha zuir gumazibar n…®ghn…®ziba, tintinibar n…®ghn…®gha onganiz…® mogh…®n ami. 
\q2 Moap…®n gumazir dapaniba puv…®ra n…®ghava agoi. 
\q2 Kenanian gumazamiziba atiatia, uan gavgavim ategha puram am…®ragha uaghiri. 
\q1  
\v 16 Me n…®n gavgavir ekiam…®n gara, atiatir ekiam ko n…®r…®zir bar ekiam me avaraz…®, me pura ikia bizitam damuan ibura. 
\q2 Me pura dag…®abar m…®n dapiagh ik…®t…®, e n…®n gumazamiziba me gitav…®ragh mangam. 
\q1 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n gumazamizir n…® me givezegha ua me iniziba, 
\q2 me guizbang…®ra kantrin kabagh itagh bar mangam. 
\q1  
\v 17 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® en aku mang…®t…®, e n…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n deraghv…®ra dapiagham. 
\q2 O Ekiam, danganir kam…®n, n…® uab…® uan d…®penim…®n ingaram. 
\q2 D…®penir n…® itir kam…®n, gumazamiziba iz…® n…®n ziam fam. 
\q1  
\v 18 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an atrivim…®n m…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Miriam…®n Onger Akam 
\p  
\v 19 Israelia nguazir dak…®rt…®zim…®n Ongarir Aghevim…®n tong…®n ghua otogha g…®fa. Ez…® Isip…®n atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, hoziaba ko gumazir karisbagh is…®n apiaziba, me Israelian g…®n zui. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ongarim gamiz…®, a uamategha iza me avara. 
\p  
\v 20 G…®n God…®n akam inigha izir amizim Miriam, an Aron…®n amezemebam, a buar mam uan dafarim…®n an suira. Amiziba bar mogh…®ra uan buaba inigha, Miriam…®n g…®n zui. Egha me buabav sogha onger akabagh amua ighiam gizi.  
\v 21 Miriam me bagha kamagh…®n ighiam bange: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God gumazir hoziabagh apiaziba, ko hoziaba sara bar me avigha 
\q2 ongarim m…®k…®nigha, apaniba ab…®nigha ziar ekiam ini. 
\q1 Kamagh…®n, ia a bagh onger akam bang…®.‚Äù 
\ms1 Israelia gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganibar arua zui 
\mr (Sapta 15:22--18:27) 
\s1 D…®par m…®sozim 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® g…®n Moses Israelian akua Ongarir Aghevim ategha, Sur…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n zui. Me gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim, aruer 3plan an arua ghua, d…®patam…®n apizir puvat…®.  
\v 23 Egha me g…®n ghua Maran danganim…®n otivigha d…®par mam bato. D…®par kam akatorim…®n aven m…®sosi, ez…® me anereman ibura. D…®par kam…®n ziam, Mara, an m…®ngarim, bizim akam…®n aven an…®nganigha m…®sosi.  
\v 24 Ez…® gumazamiziba atara m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar Moses gamua, kamagh…®n an azangs…®si, ‚ÄúE managh d…®patam amegham?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Moses Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n dia m…®gh…®gha a ko m…®geima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ter otevir mam an aka. Ez…® Moses a inigha d…®pam…®n anekuni, ez…® d…®pam ua deraz…®, me aneremam. 
\p Ez…® God danganir kam…®n arazir a ifongeziba ko bizir a damuasa m…®kemeziba me gan…®di, egh a men gan me g…®foghasa, me dar g…®n mangam, o ti puvat…®gham. 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® God me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa deragh nan akam baragh. K…®rara Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia arazir nan damazim…®n deraziba, ia dar amu. Egh ia nan Akar Gavgaviba ko arazir k…® ifongeziba bar dar g…®n mang…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, k…® paz…® ia damuan kogh…®va, ar…®mariar kurar k…® Isip…®n gumazamizibagh an…®ngiziba ia dan…®ngan kogham. Guizbang…®ra, k…® ian Ikiav…®ra Itir God. K…® ian ar…®mariaba ak…®riz…® ia ghuamazi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 27 Egha g…®n Israelia ghua Elim…®n nguibam…®n otifi. Elim, a d…®par nguazim…®n aven anagava otiva uaghirir 12pla ikia, 70plan temer detba iti.\f + \fr 15:27 \ft Temer detba mati en iruebar m…®n gara egh temer dapanibar m…®n gara det…®n ov…®ziba iti.\f* Ez…® Israelia purirpeniba, nguazim…®n aven ivemarir d…®pabar borogh…®n dar ingarigha kagh apia. 
\c 16  
\s1 Israelia daghem mana, ko kuarazibar amasa da ini 
\p  
\v 1 Israelian gumazamiziba Elim…®n danganim ategha, ghua Sen…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n otifi. Danganir kam ana Elim ko Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n tong…®ra iti. Me otivizir dughiar kamran g…®n me Isip…®n kantri ategha ghue. Egha namba 2…®n iak…®nim, an namba 15…®n dughiam…®n, me gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganir kam…®n otifi.  
\v 2 Egha me danganir kam…®n ikia Moses ko Aron…®n atara, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar aning gami.  
\v 3 Me kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n deraghai, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Isipra e m…®sueght…® e ar…®m…®ghiregh. E Isip…®n kantrin ikia dagher guar igharagha gariba uan ifongiabar da api. E m…®tiriaba sara ik…® aremeghasa gua ifonge. Egha e inigha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganir kam…®n ize.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 16:4 \xt Jon 6:31\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ia bagh bret overiam…®n anemadaght…®, an amozim…®n m…®n mag…®r…®t…® ia a iniam. Gumazamiziba dughiaba vaghvagh mang…® dughiar vam…®ra bagh…®v…®ra dagheba ini. K…® arazir kam…®n me damu gan fogh suam, me ti nan akam…®n g…®n mangam, o puvat…®gham.  
\v 5 Ez…® dughiar namba 6…®n, me dughiar pumuning bagh dagheba inigh dar ar…®kigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Moses ko Aron kamagh…®n Israelian gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúGuarat…®zim…®n ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® Isip…®n kantrin ia inigha azenan ize.  
\v 7 Ia an atara m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar a gami, ez…® an oregha g…®fa. Ia m…®zarazim…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gavgavim ko angazangarim…®n ganam. Ga pura gumazir k…®nimning. Ia manmaghsua gan atara m…®gei?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Egha Moses ua m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God uab…® guarat…®zim…®n as…®zir tuziba ia danight…® ia dar amam. Egh a m…®zarazibar bret ia danight…®, ia uan ifongiabar a iniam. An orazi ia puram a m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a dagheba ia dan…®ngam. Ez…® ga pura bizimning. Ia gan atara ga m…®geir puvat…®. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir Godra an atara a m…®gei.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Egha Moses Aron m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, bar gumazamizibar adarir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baraki. Kamagh…®n amiz…® n…® me m…®kemeght…®, me iz…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n tuifigh.‚Äù  
\v 10 Ez…® Aron me m…®g…®av…®ra itima, me kogha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganir gigim gis…®n garima, God…®n angazangarim zuam…®ra ghuariar mam…®n aven oto. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei,  
\v 12 ‚ÄúK…® Israelian adarir m…®g…®r…®g…®am baraki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® me m…®kemeght…®, me guarat…®zibar as…®zir tuzibar amam. Egh me m…®zarazibar uan ifongiam…®n bretbar amam. Me dagher kam inigh g…®vagh, me fogh suam, K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uab…® men God.‚Äù  
\v 13 Guarat…®zir kam…®n kuarazir muziarir b…®zim, m…®gha iza me itir danganim bar a giz…®fa. Ez…® m…®zarazim…®n, ghuariar d…®pam ira, danganir men itim bar a gire.  
\v 14 Ez…® ghuariar d…®pam iregha m…®s…®ngigha g…®vaz…®, me bizir muziarir av…®ribar gari da nguazim…®n iti, egha da mati terafariba m…®sigha tintinibar m…®saraghire. 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 16:15 \xt 1 Korin 10:3\x*Ez…® Israelia bizir kabar ganigha, dagh g…®fozir puvat…®. Egha me kamagh…®n uarira uarir azai, ‚ÄúKar bizir tizim?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Moses me m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar bret, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia damasa a ia gan…®ngi.  
\v 16 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akar gavgavim ia ganigha ghaze, ‚ÄòIa vaghvagh uari bagh iniva uan adarazi sara me bagh inigh. Ia vaghvagh da iniva uan gumazamiziba ko boriba bagh vaghvagh m…®ner muziaribar aghuigh.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Egha Israelia God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n me ami. Ez…® marazi bar uari bagha av…®riba iniz…®, marazi uari bagha muziaribara ini.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 16:18 \xt 2 Korin 8:15\x*Egha g…®n me dagher kabar garima, gumazamizir dagher av…®riba iniziba, men m…®neba izevezir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamizir dagher av…®riba inizir puvat…®ziba, men dagheba otevezir puvat…®. Me da apa izevegha m…®tiriam men azir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Moses me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gurum bagh dagher na taba atagh…®raghan mark…®.‚Äù  
\v 20 Ez…® gumazamizir maba Moses…®n akam baraghizir puvat…®gha, dagher nar maba am…®mzaraghan bagha da ar…®ki. Ez…® am…®mzaraghan dagher kaba apiziba dagh iz…®vaz…®ma, da puv…®ra mughasi. Ez…® Moses men atari.  
\v 21 Ez…® zurara m…®zarazibar gumazamiziba, me ifongez…® mogh…®n, uari bagha dagheba isi. Ez…® aruem anadir dughiam…®n, dagher me isir puvat…®ziba nguazim…®n ikia, d…®pam…®n m…®n otiva puram amera gefi.  
\v 22 Ez…® aruer namba 6…®n, me dughiar pumuning bagha dagheba ini. Gumazir vam…®ra m…®ner dozir pumuning pumuning gaghuiz…®, aning iz…®vafa. Ez…® Israelian gumazir dapaniba iza bizir kam…®n gun Moses m…®keme. 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 16:23 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:8-11\x*Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, gurum m…®zaraghan avughsamin dughiam. Kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam famin dughiam. Egha uaghan kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n dughiamra. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n dagher nar manaba avim…®n da tuasa, ia da tu, egh dagher nar manaba ia m…®nem…®n da isamasa, ia da isam. Eght…® nar itir kaba ia gurum m…®zaraghan bagh bar ada at…®gh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® me Moses…®n akam baregha dagher maba tue. Egha dagher nar maba tuezir puvat…®. Me am…®mzaraghan bagha da at…®z…® da iti. Ez…® dagher kaba kurizir puvat…®z…® apiziba dagh amizir puvat…®.  
\v 25 Ez…® am…®mzaraghan Moses kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n dughiam, dughiar e avughs…®va, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam famim. Ia dughiar kam…®n nguibam…®n azenan mang…® dagheba burian kogham. Kamagh amiz…®, dagher nar itir kaba, ia dar am…®.  
\v 26 Ia wigh…®n vam…®ran 6plan aruebar, dagher kaba ini. Egh namba 7…®n aruem, kar avughsamin dughiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dughiar kam…®n dagher tam nguazim…®n ikian kogham.‚Äù  
\v 27 Ez…® dughiar namba 7…®n, gumazamizir maba ghua dagheba iniasa zui. Egha me dagher tabar garir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa manad…®zogh…®n nan akaba barazir puvat…®zir arazim ategh, nan Akar Gavgavibar g…®nt…®gham?  
\v 29 Ia deraghv…®ram oragh! K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® avughsamin dughiar kam ia dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® aruer namba 6…®n, dughiar pumuning…®n damamin dagheba ia dan…®ngam. Egh aruer namba 7…®n gumazamiziba bar danganir me itiba atagh…®raghan mark…®.‚Äù  
\v 30 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me dughiar namba 7…®n ingangarir tam gamir puvat…®. Me avughsi. 
\p  
\v 31 \x - \xo 16:31 \xt D…®boboniba 11:7-8\x*Ez…® Israelian gumazamiziba dagher kam kamagh…®n a d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúMana.‚Äù\f + \fr 16:31 \ft Hibrun akam…®n, ziar kam ‚Äúmana,‚Äù a m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam ko mong magh ghu, ‚ÄúKar bizir tizim?‚Äù N…® sapta 16:15…®n gan.\f* Hibrun akam…®n Manan kam…®n ganganim, temer ov…®zir muziarim…®n m…®n gara egha ghurghuri. Egha an is…®ngt…®zim, mati bisket…®n me hani sara ingarizim. 
\p  
\v 32 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòE m…®ner tam inigh, an manabar aghuam. Eght…® an en g…®n otivamin ovavir boriba bagh ikiam. Me g…®n an gan suam, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God e gan…®ngizir daghem. A Isip…®n kantrin e inigha azenan iza gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n e at…®zir dughiam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 33 \x - \xo 16:33 \xt Hibru 9:4\x*Egha Moses Aron m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nguazir m…®ner tam inigh, manan tabar aghuigh. Egh m…®nem is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n anet…®gh. Eght…® borir g…®n otivighamiba, a g…®fogham.‚Äù  
\v 34 Ez…® Aron manan dagher m…®ner kam isa, g…®n izamin dughiam bagha, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Boksiam borogh…®n anet…®, ez…® Aron Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®ram ami.  
\v 35 \x - \xo 16:35 \xt Josua 5:12; Nehemia 9:20-21; Jon 6:31\x*Ez…® Israelia manan dagher kam apa ghua 40plan azenibar tu. Ez…® 40plan azeniba g…®vaz…®ma me ghua Kenanian kantrin otivigha, kantrin kam gapiagha uari bagha azenibar ingari.  
\v 36 (Dughiar kam…®n Israelia bizibar os…®mt…®zibagh fofoghamin skel…®n pumuning iti. Omer ko Epah, mam m…®ner dozir vam…®ran m…®n iti. Mam 10plan m…®ner dozibar m…®n iti.) 
\c 17  
\s1 Me dag…®am…®n d…®pam ini 
\r (D…®boboniba 20:1-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Israelian gumazamiziba bar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n g…®n ghua, d…®kavigha Sen…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim ategha zui. Egh dughiar manam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemeght…®, me d…®kavigh…®va danganir me itir kam ategh s…®vaghs…®vagh mang…® danganir igharazir mam dapiagham. Me kamagh…®ra apiaghira ghua, g…®n me ghua Refidim…®n danganim…®n otogha, purirpenibar ingarigha apia. Ez…® danganir kam d…®par damamiba puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® gumazamiziba Moses…®n atara ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® e damamin d…®patam e dan…®ngigh.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® a men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha nan atari? Ia masa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Araziba tuis…®gha, an gavgavim bagha azai? Ia ti n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® gumazamiziba d…®pam bagha kuariba bar me m…®s…®ngiz…®, me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar Moses gimoba ghuav…®ra iti. Egha me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha Isip…®n kantrin aven e inigha azenan ize? N…® ti kamagh…®n ifonge, e uan boriba ko as…®ziba, e damamin d…®paba puvat…®gh, kagh ar…®ghiregham, a?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Moses pamten kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamizir kaba dag…®abar na ginivigh, na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghasa. Ez…® k…® manmagh me damuam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Israelian gumazir dapanitaba inigh, ia daru gumazamizibar faragh mang…®. Ia darus…®va, asadivir aghorir n…® faragha Nail…®n Fanem m…®soghezim sara inigh mang…®.  
\v 6 K…® Horep…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n dag…®atam gis…®n tugh ikiam, kar Sainain M…®ghs…®am. N…® rogh…®ra iz…®va, asadivir aghorir kam…®n dag…®am m…®sokegh. Eght…® d…®pam an otogh azenan fasfagh ir…®t…®, gumazamiziba anemam.‚Äù Ez…® Israelian gumazir dapaniba gari, Moses kamagh…®n amiz…®, d…®pam otogha izaghiri.  
\v 7 Ez…® me danganir kam kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúMasa,‚Äù an m…®ngarim kamak…®n, ‚ÄúTuighs…®zir Arazim,‚Äù ko ‚ÄúMeriba,‚Äù an m…®ngarim, ‚ÄúAdarim.‚Äù Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, Israelia atara ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, e ko iti, o puvat…®.‚Äù Arazir kam…®n, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Araziba tuis…®gha an gavgavim bagha azangs…®si. 
\s1 Israelia Amalekia ko m…®sosi 
\p  
\v 8 Egha g…®n Amalekia iza Refidim…®n danganim…®n Israelia ko m…®sosi.  
\v 9 Ez…® Moses kamagh…®n Josua m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® e bagh gumazitaba am…®seveght…®, me gurum…®n mang…® Amalekia ko m…®sogh. Eght…® k…® mang…® m…®ghs…®ar dozir munam…®n tugh, God…®n gavgavim itir asadivir aghorim…®n suiragham.‚Äù  
\v 10 Ez…® Josua, Moses a m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, gumazir maba inigha ghua Amalekia ko m…®sosi. Ez…® Moses, Aron ko Hur sara, me m…®ghs…®ar dozim…®n uanabo.  
\v 11 Egha Moses uan agharimning feghav…®ra itima, Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba, Amalekia gafigha ghuav…®ra iti. Ez…® Moses uan agharimning ataghiz…® aning uaghirima, Amalekia Israelia gafiragha ghuav…®ra iti.  
\v 12 Ez…® g…®n Moses…®n agharimning a girima, a uam aning ghufan ibura. Ez…® Aron ko Hur dag…®ar mam inigha anefaz…®, Moses a gapera. Ez…® aning Moses…®n borogh…®n vong ko vong…®n tugha, an agharimning suiragha aning gifueghav…®ra ikia, kamagh…®ra ikiav…®ra itima, aruem ghuaghir…®.  
\v 13 Ez…® Josua uan adarazi ko Amalekian m…®dorozir gumaziba ab…®nigha, bar me gas…®ghas…®ki. 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 17:14 \xt God…®n Araziba 25:17-19; 1 Samuel 15:2-9\x*Ez…® g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® akar kam ak…®nafaritam…®n an osiright…®, gumazamiziba a g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Akar kam kamak…®n, ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Amalekia bar me ag…®vagham. Eght…® gumazamiziba ua me g…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham.‚Äô N…® akar kam Josua bagh a d…®pont…®, an a barakigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, Moses ofa gamir dakozir mam…®n ingari. Ez…® ofa gamir dakozir kam…®n ziam mati nir av…®zir ekiam me an osirigha a ghufez…® a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, nan akuraz…® k…® uan apaniba ab…®ra.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Moses ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n inir av…®zim ghufegh bar p…®n an suiragh.\f + \fr 17:16 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, zurara Amalekia ko m…®sogh kamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\c 18  
\s1 Jetro iza Moses…®n gari 
\p  
\v 1 Jetro, a Midianian ofa gamir gumazim, a Moses…®n amerem. A bizir God Israelia ko Moses bagha amizibar eghaghanim baregha, uaghan dughiar Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan gumazamiziba, Israelia, me inigha Isip ategha izezir eghaghanim baraki.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 18:2-3 \xt Ua Me Ini 2:21-22\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Jetro Moses…®n ganasa ize. Moses faragha uan amuim Sipora amadaz…®, a uan afeziam Jetro bagha ghu.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 18:3 \xt Aposel 7:29\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, Sipora ko Moses…®n otarir pumuning…®n ko Jetro, me izava otifi. An otarimning…®n ziamning, Gersom ko Elieser. Moses faragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® kantrin igharazim…®n gumazim, egha kantrin igharazim…®n iti.‚Äù Egha a uan otarir ivariam ziam, ‚ÄúGersom,‚Äù a gat…®.\f + \fr 18:3 \ft Hibrun akam…®n, ziar kam, ‚ÄúGersom,‚Äù a mong kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúKantrin igharazim…®n gumazim.‚Äù\f* 
\p  
\v 4 Egha a g…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan afeziam…®n God nan akuraz…®, Isip…®n atrivim na m…®soghez…® k…® aremezir puvat…®.‚Äù Egha uan otarir dozim, a ‚ÄúElieser,‚Äù a gat…®.\f + \fr 18:4 \ft Hibrun akam…®n, ziar kam, ‚ÄúElieser,‚Äù a mong kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúGod nan akura.‚Äù\f* 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Jetro, Moses…®n amuim ko an otarir pumuning…®n akua me iza gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim iza, God…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®ra izava otifi. Kar Moses purirpenibar ingarigha dar ikezir danganim.  
\v 6 Egha Jetro kamagh…®n Moses bagha akam amada, ‚ÄúK…® n…®n amerem Jetro, k…® n…®n amuim ko n…®n otarimning, e n…® bagha ize.‚Äù  
\v 7 Ez…® Moses akar kam baregha, ghua tuavim…®n Jetro bato. Egha Moses aviragha g…®n ghua an tori. Egha aning uan ik…®r…®m…®rim bagha uaning…®n azangs…®gha, me g…®n Moses…®n purirpenim…®n aven ghue.  
\v 8 Egha Moses uan amerem bizir av…®ribar a geghara ghaze, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian akurvaghasa, Isip…®n atrivim ko Isip…®n gumazamizibagh amiz…®, arazarazir av…®riba otifi. Egha a ghaze, me tuavim…®n zuima, bizir kuraba ko os…®mt…®ziba me bativima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God men akura. 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Jetro akar kam baregha fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bizir aghuaribar Israelia gamigha, Isipian dafarim…®n ua me ini. Ez…® Jetro akar kam baregha bar akonge.  
\v 10 Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe. A Isip…®n atrivim ko an gumazamizibar dafarim…®n ia inigha ian akuraz…®, ia kalabus…®n ingangarir kurar kam ataki.  
\v 11 Ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, Ekiam bar god…®n igharazibagh afiragha kamagh…®n ami. Isipia akaba batoghava paza ia gamima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian akura. Ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar gavgaviz…®, an gavgavim god…®n igharazibar gavgavibagh afira.‚Äù  
\v 12 Egha Jetro ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rizir mam, inigha God gan…®di. Egha uaghan ofan igharaziba God gan…®ngi. Ez…® Aron ko Israelian gumazir dapaniba iza, God…®n damazim…®n Moses…®n amerem koma api. 
\s1 Me os…®mt…®ziba tuis…®ghamin gumazamizir maba am…®sefe 
\r (God…®n Araziba 1:9-18) 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Dughiar igharazim…®n, Moses am…®mzaraghan jas…®n m…®n aperagha Israelian gumazamizibar os…®mt…®ziba tuis…®si. Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba Moses bagha m…®zarazim…®n izav…®ra ikia, ghua guarat…®zim…®n tu.  
\v 14 Ez…® Jetro, Moses gumazamizibar akurvazir araziba, bar dar gara, egha kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúManing, gua uaningra ingangarir av…®ribar gumazamizibar akurvaghasa dagh ami. N…® uab…®ra ingangarir kam damuan mark…®. N…® gan, n…® os…®mt…®ziba ak…®ra aperaghav…®ra iti gumazamiziba m…®zaraghara iza n…® ko m…®k…®masa, n…® m…®zua tuivighav ikia, ghua aruem g…®fa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Moses a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamiziba bizir God damuasa ifongezibagh fofoghasa, na bagha izi.  
\v 16 Gumazitamning bizir mam bagh uaning…®n atarigh, aning na bagh izeght…®, k…® aning…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregh aning…®n os…®mt…®zim ak…®ram. Egh k…® arazir God ifongeziba ko God…®n akabar men sure damuam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Jetro kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan amerem, n…® ingangarir kam damuamin tuavir aghuim…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 18 Ingangarir kam bar n…®n ekefe. N…® uab…®ra a damu mang…®t…® n…®n m…®karzim n…®n am…®ragham. Eght…® gumazamiziba uaghan men m…®karziba men am…®ragham.  
\v 19 N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nan akam baraght…®, k…® tuavir aghuarir mam n…® m…®k…®mam. Eght…® God n…® ko ikiam. Arazir kam deragham, n…® gumazamiziba bagh God…®n damazim…®n abuir gumazim…®n m…®n ik…®. Egh men m…®g…®r…®g…®ar me uari adoziba, n…® da inigh a bagh mang…®.  
\v 20 Egh n…® arazir God ifongeziba ko God…®n akabar men sure damuva, tuavir me g…®n mangamim…®n me m…®k…®m…®va, arazir me zurara damuamim…®n men sure damu.  
\v 21 Egh n…® uaghan fofozir gumazir aghuitaba m…®seveght…®, me gumazamizibar dapanibar ikiam. Eght…® tarazi 1,000plan gumazamizibar gant…®ma, tarazi 100plan gumazamizibar gant…®ma, tarazi 50plan gant…®ma, tarazi 10plan ganam. Gumazir kaba uari ab…®nigh guizbang…®ra God…®n atiating…®va an apengan ik…®, egh gumazir e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim men itibar, m…®n ik…®. Gumazamiziba dag…®aba me dan…®ng, me gekut…®, me arazir kurabar amuan kogham.  
\v 22 Eght…® gumazir kaba jasbar m…®n ik…®, gumazamizibar os…®mt…®ziba tuis…®gham. Egh me uari os…®mt…®zir muziariba tuis…®gham. Egh os…®mt…®zir ekiaba, me da inigh n…® bagh iz…®t…®, n…® da tuis…®gham. Egh me n…®n akuragh ingangarir kam…®n os…®mt…®zim inight…®, ingangarim n…®n osemeghan kogham.  
\v 23 K…® bizir God n…® damuasa a ifongeziba k…® dar gun n…® m…®keme, n…® dar amu. N…® nan akam…®n g…®n mang…®, eght…® ingangarir kam n…® damight…®, n…®n m…®karzim n…®n am…®raghan kogham. Eght…® ia gumazamizibar os…®mt…®ziba ko akabar k…®right…®, me navir am…®riziba ik…®, egh uamategh uan purirpenibar mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® Moses, Jetron akar aghuir kam baregha kamagh…®n ami.  
\v 25 Egha a Israelian tong…®n fofozir gumazir aghuariba m…®sevegha me at…®z…®, me gumazamizibar gumazir dapanibar m…®n iti. Ez…® men marazi 1,000plan gumazamizibar garima, marazi 100plan gumazamizibar garima, marazi 50plan garima, marazi 10plan gari.  
\v 26 Egha me zurara jasbar m…®n os…®mt…®zibar tuis…®ghamin ingangarim gami. Me uari araziba ko os…®mt…®zir muziariba tuis…®si, egha os…®mt…®zir ekiaba, Moses bagha da amadi. Ez…® a uab…® da tuis…®gha dar k…®ri.  
\v 27 Ez…® bizir kabar g…®n, Moses uan amerem Jetron dafarim…®n suiraz…®, Jetro uamategha uan nguibam…®n zui. 
\c 19  
\ms1 God Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim  // Israelia ko a gami 
\mr (Sapta 19--31) 
\s1 Israelia iza Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n iti 
\p  
\v 1-2 Ez…® Israelia Refidim…®n danganim ategha zui. Me ghua Sainain gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n otifi. Me otivizir dughiar kamra, a iak…®nir me Isip…®n kantri ataghizim…®n g…®n ghua, iak…®nir pumuning g…®vaz…®, iak…®nir namba 3 otoz…®, me an aruer namba 1…®n Sainain otifi. Egha me Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n purirpenibar ingarigha apia.  
\v 3 Ez…® Moses God ko m…®k…®masa m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuanadi. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®ghs…®am…®n ikia Moses…®n d…®agha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® Israelia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba me dan…®ngam, me Jekop…®n ovavir boriba.  
\v 4 K…® Isip…®n amizir biziba, ia uari dar ganigha g…®fa. Egha ia nan gari k…® ia ini, mati kuarazir bagam uan nguzim uan av…®zim…®n a isi mogh…®n, k…® ua bagha ia inigha iza danganir kam…®n izez…®, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n na ko iti.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 19:5 \xt God…®n Araziba 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; 26:18; Taitus 2:14\x*\x - \xo 19:5-6 \xt 1 Pita 2:9\x*Egh ia dat…®r…®gh…®n nan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n suiragh gavgavigh, nan akabar g…®n mang…®, nan gumazamizibar otogham. Nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar, ko gumazamiziba bar, me nan adarazira, eght…® k…® men tong…®n iarara ua bagh ia m…®sevegham, eght…® ia nan gumazamizibara ikiam.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 19:6 \xt Akar Mogomem 1:6; 5:10\x*Egh ia na baghav…®ra itir gumazamizibara ik…®, egh ofa gamir gumazibar m…®n ik…®, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba bagh abuir gumazim…®n ingangarim damuam. Egh ia bar guizbang…®ra nan gumazamizibara ik…®va na baghv…®ra ikiam.‚Äù Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba gumazamizibar an…®ngasa Moses m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Moses m…®ghs…®am ategha ghua Israelian gumazir dapaniba akuvagha, akar Ikiav…®ra Itir God a m…®kemeziba, bar dar gun me m…®gei.  
\v 8 Ez…® gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God e m…®kemeziba, e bar dar amuam.‚Äù Ez…® Moses ghua gumazamizibar akabar gun Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh. K…® ghuariar m…®tiar p…®zim…®n aven k…® ia bagh iz…®va, n…® ko m…®k…®mam. Dughiar kam…®n gumazamiziba oraght…®, k…® n…® ko m…®k…®mam. Eght…® me dat…®r…®gh…®n ikegh mang…®, me zurara n…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dar ikiam.‚Äù Ez…® Moses gumazamizibar akabar gun, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® gumazamizibav k…®m suam, me dat…®r…®gh…®n ikegh mang…® gurum…®n, me uari na dan…®ng…®s…® uan n…®ghn…®ziba ko araziba ak…®righ, bar zuegh. Egh me uan korotiaba ruegh, nan ziam f…®s…® uari ak…®righ.  
\v 11 Me uari ak…®righ tugh gavgavigh ik…® mang…® aruer namba 3…®n otogh. Dughiar kam, k…® Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n izighir…® gumazamiziba bar, men damazim…®n otogham.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 19:12-13 \xt Hibru 12:18-20\x*Egh n…® m…®ghs…®am bagh m…®taghniam at…®gh. Eght…® gumazamiziba m…®taghniar kam…®n vong…®n mangan mark…®. N…® deraghv…®ra me m…®k…®m, me deraghv…®ra ganigh, me m…®taghniar kam…®n ikiavk…®nigh vong…®n mang…®, m…®ghs…®am…®n mavanangan kogham. Guizbang…®ra me m…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®ra mangan k…® anogoroke. Gumazitam m…®taghniam…®n ikiavk…®night…®, me a m…®sueght…® an aremegham.  
\v 13 Egh me dafaribar an suiragh a m…®sueght…® an aremeghan mark…®. Me dag…®abar a ginifigh, o afuzitam…®n a b…®ragh. Gumazitam, o as…®zitam m…®taghniam…®n ikiavk…®night…®, ia arazir kam bagh a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Ia dughiar vam…®ran, ia m…®ghs…®am…®n anang. Ia s…®gham baraghamin dughiam, ia mang…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Moses m…®ghs…®am ategha uaghir…®gha gumazamizibav m…®keme. Ez…® me an akam baregha, me uari God dan…®ngasa uan n…®ghn…®ziba ko araziba ak…®righa, egha zue. Me uan korotiaba ruegha God…®n ziam fer arazim damuasa uari ak…®raghasi.  
\v 15 Ez…® Moses me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa zuerim bagh uari ak…®r tugh gavgavigh ik…®. Egh dat…®r…®gh…®n ikegh mang…® zuerim…®n, ia amiziba ko dakuan mark…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 19:16 \xt Akar Mogomem 4:5\x*\x - \xo 19:16-18 \xt God…®n Araziba 4:11-12\x*Ez…® dughiar namba 3…®n m…®zarazim…®n arariba dagarvazi on…®mariba taghtazima, ghuariar m…®tiar p…®zir mam izaghira m…®ghs…®am avara. Ez…® me s…®ghar ararer gavgavir mam baraki. Egha gumazamizir danganir kam…®n itiba, bar atiatigha n…®si.  
\v 17 Ez…® Moses gumazamiziba inigha, me itir danganim…®n azenan ghua men faragha ghua God bativasa zui. Me m…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n ghua, an apengan zarim…®n tuifi.  
\v 18 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God avim…®n aven ikia, egha izaghira Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n iti, ez…® m…®gharir ekiam m…®ghs…®am bar anevara. M…®gharir kam ghuavanaga, mati avir ekiam…®n m…®gharim ghuavanadi. Ez…® m…®k…®mk…®zir ekiam m…®ghs…®am…®n oto.  
\v 19 Ez…® s…®gham…®n ararem bar ekevegha pamtem ara ghuav…®ra iti. Ez…® Moses God m…®gei. Ez…® God a ikarvazi, an tiarim mati ararim dagarvasi.  
\v 20 Ikiav…®ra Itir God izaghira Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n orazim…®n ikia, egha Moses…®n dei. Ez…® Moses ghuavanadi. 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mag…®r…®, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim gumazamizibar an…®ngight…® me m…®taghniar kam…®n ikiavk…®nigh iz…® nan ganan mark…®. Me kamagh…®n damigh, men av…®riba ar…®ghiregham.  
\v 22 Nan borogh…®n izir ofa gamir gumaziba, me uaghan uari na dan…®ng…®s…®, uari ak…®righ nan damazim…®n zuegham. Puvat…®ght…®, k…® ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Egha Moses Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® akar gavgavim e gan…®ngi, kamagh…®n gumazamiziba m…®ghs…®am…®n mangan kogham. E m…®taghniam ar…®gha m…®ghs…®am…®n ap…®nim ighuigha, e kamagh…®n fo, m…®ghs…®ar kam, a n…®n m…®ghs…®amra, egha ana anogoroke.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mag…®r…®, Aron inight…® a n…® ko uamategh anang. Eght…® ofa gamir gumaziba ko, gumazamiziba bar m…®taghniar kam…®n ikiavk…®nigh na bagh m…®ghs…®am…®n anangan mark…®. Me kamagh…®n damight…®, k…® ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam.‚Äù  
\v 25 Ez…® Moses akar kam baregha gumazamizibar bighan iraghugha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar me m…®gei. 
\c 20  
\s1 God…®n 10plan Akar Gavgaviba 
\r (God…®n Araziba 5:1-21) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® God kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\b  
\li1  
\v 2 K…® uab…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God. K…®rara Isip…®n kantrin ia inigha ian akua azenan ize. Kar danganir ia ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar ikezim. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 3 Ia bar narara g…®n mang…® nan ziamra fam. Egh ia asetam…®n g…®n mangan bar mark…®. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 4 \x - \xo 20:4-5 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:17; Ofa Gami 19:4; 26:1; God…®n Araziba 4:15-18; 27:15\x*Ia uari bagh marvir guatam an ingaran mark…®. Ia overiam…®n itir bizitam, ko nguazim…®n itir bizitam ko d…®pam…®n aven itir biziba, ia bizir kabar gan, dar m…®n marvir guatam…®n ingaran mark…®.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 20:5-6 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:6-7; D…®boboniba 14:18; God…®n Araziba 7:9-10\x*Ia asetam ko marvir guatam…®n itevibar p…®r…®va an ziam fan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ian God. Egh god…®n ifavaritam…®n amamangat…®ght…®, a nan danganim inian kogham. Bar puvat…®. Gumazamizir nan aghuaziba, me os…®mt…®zim iti, ez…® k…® ivezir kuram me ko men ik…®zim dan…®ng mang…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, men ik…®zim…®n igiar boriba ko az…®ziba otogham.  
\v 6 Ez…® gumazamizir bar na gifongeziba, me nan Akar Gavgavibar g…®n zui. K…® bar ian ovavir boriba men apangkuvigh kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®, men 1,000…®n ovavir borir g…®n izamibar otogham. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 7 \x - \xo 20:7 \xt Ofa Gami 19:12\x*Nan ziam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God, ia puram a d…®ponan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, gumazamizir pura nan ziam d…®boriba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n me m…®k…®man kogham, pura bizim, me os…®mt…®ziba pu. Bar puvat…®, a ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 8 \x - \xo 20:8 \xt Ua Me Ini 16:23-30; 31:12-14\x*Ia Sabat…®n dughiam deragh a g…®n…®ghn…®gh m…®k…®m suam, a dughiar k…® ua bagha inabazimra ikiam.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 20:9-10 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:12; 31:15; 34:21; 35:2; Ofa Gami 23:3\x*Ia wigh…®n vam…®ra, 6plan aruebar aven ingangariba bar dar amuam.  
\v 10 Ez…® namba 7…®n dughiam, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n dughiamra. Kar dughiar ia avughsamim. Egh Sabat…®n dughiam, ia bar ingangaribar amuan mark…®. Ia uan otariba, guiviba, ingangarir gumaziba, ingangarir amiziba, as…®ziba, ko ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamizir iza ian nguibam…®n itiba, ia bar ingangaribar amuan kogham.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 20:11 \xt Jenesis 2:1-3; Ua Me Ini 31:17\x*Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God 6plan aruebar nguazim ko overiam, ongarim…®n ko dar itir biziba bar adar ingari. Egha namba 7…®n aruem an avughse. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Sabat…®n dughiam deraghav…®ra a g…®n…®ghn…®gha an anogorogha a gamiz…®ma, an a baghv…®ra ikiamin dughiam…®n oto. Kar God…®n dughiamra. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 12 \x - \xo 20:12 \xt God…®n Araziba 27:16; Matyu 15:4; 19:19; Mak 7:10; 10:19; Luk 18:20; Efesus 6:2-3\x*Egh ia vaghvagh uan afeziam ko amebam…®n apengan ik…®, men akabar g…®n mang…®. Ia kamagh…®n damigh…®va, ia dughiar ruarim…®n nguazir kam…®n ikiam, kar nguazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God a isa ia gan…®dim. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 13 \x - \xo 20:13 \xt Jenesis 9:6; Ofa Gami 24:17; Matyu 5:21; 19:18; Mak 10:19; Luk 18:20; Rom 13:9; Jems 2:11\x*Egh ia gumazamizir igharazibav soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiran mark…®. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 14 \x - \xo 20:14 \xt Ofa Gami 20:10; Matyu 5:27; 19:18; Mak 10:19; Luk 18:20; Rom 13:9; Jems 2:11\x*Egh ia poroghamiba uari bak…®a uari ko akuir arazim damuan mark…®. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 15 \x - \xo 20:15 \xt Ofa Gami 19:11; Matyu 19:18; Mak 10:19; Luk 18:20; Rom 13:9\x*Egh ia biziba ok…®man mark…®. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 16 \x - \xo 20:16 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:1; Matyu 19:18; Mak 10:19; Luk 18:20\x*Egh ia ifavarir akabav k…®m…®va gumazamizir igharazitam…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®ghan mark…®. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 17 \x - \xo 20:17 \xt Rom 7:7; 13:9\x*Egh ia gumazir igharazitam…®n d…®penim bagh navim d…®kavan mark…®. Egh an amuim bagh navim d…®kavan mark…®. Egh an ingangarir gumazim, ingangarir amizim, bulmakau, donki, ko an bizir igharaziba bar, da bagh navim d…®kavan mark…®. 
\s1 Gumazamiziba God…®n atiatingi 
\r (God…®n Araziba 5:22-23) 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 20:18-19 \xt Hibru 12:18-19\x*Ez…® gumazamiziba gara orazima, ararim pamtem dagarvazima, s…®gham araima, on…®marim taghtazima, m…®gharir ekiam m…®ghs…®am avara. Ez…® me bar atiatigha puv…®ra n…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me s…®vagha ghua m…®ghs…®am…®n saghon tuifi.  
\v 19 Egha me kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uab…® e m…®k…®mt…® e n…® baragham. God e m…®k…®mt…®, e ar…®m…®ghiregham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® Moses me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa atiatingan mark…®. God kamaghsua ifonge, ia bar an atiatigh an apengan ik…®, egh arazir kurabar amuan kogham. Kamagh…®n a iza ian navir averiabagh foghasa, da guizbang…®ra a baghav…®ra iti, o puvat…®.‚Äù  
\v 21 Egha gumazamiziba saghon tuivighav…®ra itima, Moses uab…®ra ghua God aven itir ghuariar p…®zim…®n borogh…®n zui. 
\s1 Ofa gamir dakozim…®n araziba 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n Israelia akar kabar me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa uari ganigha kamagh…®n fo, k…® Uan Nguibam…®n ikia, ia ko m…®keme.  
\v 23 Ia orakigh. Ia gol ko silvan asebar marvir guabar ingar, dar ziaba fan mark…®. K…® uab…®ra, ia bar nan ziamra fam.  
\v 24 Ia nguazitaba inigh na bagh ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingar. Egh ofa gamir dakozir kamnang gis…®n, ia sipsipba ko bulmakauba ofan m…®n da is…® na dan…®ngigh, ofan taba, kar ia da tueght…® da bar isi m…®gh…®righamin ofaba. Eght…® taba, kar ia gumazamiziba na ko navir vam…®ran ikiasava amir ofaba. Egh ia danganir k…® inabazibar kamagh…®n nan ziam f…®t…®, k…® iz…® deragh ia damuam.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 20:25 \xt God…®n Araziba 27:5-7; Josua 8:31\x*Ia ofa gamir dag…®ar dakozim…®n ingar, egh dag…®ar gumaziba d…®ghoreziba inian mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, ia ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingars…®, dag…®ar tuizim…®n dag…®ar ekiatam am…®neght…®, arazir kam…®n dag…®ar kam nan damazim…®n zueghan koght…®, nan ingangarim bar deraghan kogham.  
\v 26 Ia ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingaright…® a p…®n ik…®t…®, ia ad…®r…®ziam…®n ingarigh mavanang, egh arazir kam…®n ofa damuan mark…®. Bar mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n damigh, ad…®r…®ziam…®n mavanangt…®, me ti ian m…®karzir mogomebar ganigham. Arazir kam derazir puvat…®.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\c 21  
\s1 Hibrun ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar garir araziba 
\r (God…®n Araziba 15:12-18) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Israelia damuamin arazibar gun me m…®k…®m:  
\v 2 \x - \xo 21:2-6 \xt Ofa Gami 25:39-46\x*Ia Hibruian gumazitam ingangarir gumazir k…®nitam…®n m…®n a givezeght…®, a ian ingangaribar amu mang…®, 6plan azenibar tugh. Egh namba 7…®n azenim…®n ia aneteght…® a mang…®. Egh a dag…®ar taba ia dan…®ngan mark…®. Bar mark…®.  
\v 3 A faragha odiarim…®n ikia n…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n oto, egh a g…®n mang…®s…®, a uab…®ra mang…®. A faraghav…®ra amuim…®n ikia n…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n oto, egh dughiar a n…® ateghamim, a uan amuim inigh a sara mangam.  
\v 4 Egh an gumazir dapanim amizim a danight…®, a boriba bateght…®, amizir kam uan boriba ko, me uan gumazir dapanim ko ikiam. Eght…® gumazimra f…®righ…®r…®gh mangam. 
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúEgh ingangarir gumazim suam, ‚ÄòK…® uan gumazir dapanim gifongegha, uan amuim ko boribagh ifongegha, me atagh…®raghan aghua,‚Äô  
\v 6 eght…® an gumazir dapanim a inigh God…®n D…®penim…®n mang…®. Egh ingangarir gumazim tiar akam o temer tiar akam…®n m…®riam…®n asaraghav itim…®n borogh…®n tugh…®v ik…®. Eght…® an gumazir dapanim d…®konir tam inigh, egh an kuarim okoregham. Arazir kam…®n a gumazir dapanir kam…®n ingangarir gumazir k…®nimra ik…® mang…®t…®, an ovevem…®n dughiam otogham. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúEgh gumazitam uan guivim ingangarir amizir k…®nim…®n m…®n anemadaght…®, gumazir dapanim a givezeght…®, g…®n namba 6…®n azenim g…®vaght…®, an aneteght…® a ingangarim ateghan kogham. Ia ingangarir gumazibagh ami mogh…®n, ingangarir amizibar amuan kogham.  
\v 8 Gumazim ingangarir amizitam givezegh, uan amuir dozim…®n m…®n an ik…®s…®, ua g…®n uan amuir dozir kam…®n aghuagh…®va, uam an afeziam…®n teght…® a uam a givezegham. Gumazir kam arazir aghuim…®n amizir kam gamizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n a kantrin igharazitam…®n gumaziba bagh anemang…®t…® me a givezan mark…®.  
\v 9 Egh gumazir kam uan otarim g…®n…®ghn…®gh ingangarir amizir k…®nir kam a dan…®ng…®s…®, a deraghv…®ra uan guivim…®n m…®n a damu.  
\v 10 Egh gumazir dapanim amizir igharazim…®n ik…®s…®, a ingangarir amizir a faragha ikezir kam, deragh a damu. A faraghav…®ra a gami mogh…®n, dagheba ko korotiaba a dan…®ng, egh a ko dakuv…®ra ik…®.  
\v 11 An arazir 3plan kabar amuan kogh, egh pura amizir kam ateght…® a mang…®. Gumazim uab…® gives…® a m…®k…®man mark…®.‚Äù 
\s1 M…®doroziba ak…®ramin araziba 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 21:12 \xt Ofa Gami 24:17\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam pamten gumazitam m…®sueght…®, an aremeght…®, ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 21:13 \xt D…®boboniba 35:10-34; God…®n Araziba 19:1-13; Josua 20:1-9\x*Eght…® a gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremeghan n…®ghn…®zim ikian koght…®, Godra gumazir kam ateght…® an an agharim…®n paz…® a damut…®ma an aremegham, eght…® gumazir a m…®soghezim an ar…® mang…® nguibar k…® ia bagha m…®sevezim…®n mang…®gh, egh a deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 14 Eght…® gumazitam gumazir igharazim bagh navim ikuvigh, a m…®sueght…® ana aremeghs…® n…®ghn…®gham, ia a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. An ar…® mang…® nan ofa gamir dakozim…®n ik…®t…®, ia a inigh danganir igharazitam…®n mang…®gh, a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. 
\p  
\v 15 ‚ÄúEgh gumazitam uan afeziam ko amebam m…®suegham, ia a m…®sueght…® an aremegh.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 21:16 \xt God…®n Araziba 24:7\x*Eght…® tav gumazitam okemegh, a damight…® an an ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n ikiam, o gumazir igharazim ateght…® an a givezegham, ia gumazir arazir kam gamizim m…®sueght…® an aremegh.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 21:17 \xt Ofa Gami 20:9; Matyu 15:4; Mak 7:10\x*Eght…® gumazitam uan afeziam ko amebam paz…®va aning…®n atar…®va aning…®n ziamning gas…®ghasight…®, ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh.  
\v 18-19 Ez…® gumazitamning uaning…®n atar…®va, egh tav dafarim medagh, tav m…®suegham, o dag…®atam…®n tav b…®ragh, a m…®sueght…® an aremeghan koght…®, ia gumazir kam…®n arazir kuram ikarvaghan mark…®. Eght…® gumazir os…®mt…®zir ekiam inizir kam, a dakozim…®n ik…®, egh g…®n a d…®kavigh asadivir aghorim…®n suiragh daruam. Eght…® gumazir a m…®soghezir kam dag…®ar taba a givezam. Eght…® dag…®ar kaba gumazir kam…®n ingangarim ataghizir dughiabagh ivezam. Gumazir a m…®soghezir kam a geghuv mang…® dughiar a ua deraghamim otogham.  
\v 20 Ez…® gumazitam aghorim inigh uan ingangarir gumazim o ingangarir amizir k…®nim m…®sueght…®, ingangarir gumazim o amizim dughiar kamra bizir kam bagh aremeght…®, ia ivezir kuram gumazir dapanir kam a dan…®ngam.  
\v 21 Eght…® gumazim o amizir kam dughiar vam…®ra o pumuning…®n ikegh g…®n aremeght…®, ia an gumazir dapanim ivezir kuram a dan…®ngan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, ingangarir gumazim, kar an gumazir dapanim…®n bizimra, eght…® ovengezir gumazim dat…®r…®gh…®n an ingangarim damuan kogham.  
\v 22 Eght…® gumazitaba uariv sogh…®va amizir navim asangizim m…®sueght…®, a borir kuam bateght…®, amebam deraght…®, gumazir amizim m…®soghezir kam, an pam ifongez…® mogh…®n gumazir kam dag…®abar uan os…®mt…®zim ak…®ram. Eght…® araziba tuis…®zir gumazim dag…®ar kabar amamangat…®ght…®, g…®n amizir kam…®n pam da iniam.  
\v 23 Eght…® amizim os…®mt…®zim inight…®, ia bizir kam ikaragh os…®mt…®zim gumazir a m…®soghezim dat…®gh. Amizim aremeght…®, ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 21:24 \xt Ofa Gami 24:19-20; God…®n Araziba 19:21; Matyu 5:38\x*Egh an damazim, atarim, agharim, o suem ikuvight…®, ia kamagh…®ra da ikarvagh.  
\v 25 Eght…® gumazim amizir kam avim…®n an m…®karzim daboroght…®, ia an m…®karzim daborogh. Eght…® an an m…®karzim gas…®ghas…®ght…® duam otoght…®, ia kamagh…®ra a ikaragh. Egh a benim…®n a m…®sueght…®, kamagh…®ra ia benim…®n a ikaragh.  
\v 26 Egh gumazitam uan ingangarir gumazim o ingangarir amizim damazim m…®sueght…® a ikuvight…®, a ua an ingangarir gumazim o amizim…®n m…®n ikian kogham. Gumazir kam aneteght…® a mang…®. Kar damazir as…®ghas…®zir ivezim.  
\v 27 Egh a ingangarir gumazim o amizim m…®sogh…®va an atarim asigh, egh aneteght…® a mang…®. Kar atarim…®n ivezim.‚Äù 
\s1 Bulmakaun arazir kuram, ak…®ramin araziba 
\p  
\v 28 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBulmakaun tam uan kom…®n gumazitam o amizitam b…®raght…® an aremeght…®, ia bulmakaun kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Eght…® ia an tuzim aman mark…®. Eght…® bulmakaun ghuavim, an os…®mt…®zim inian kogham.  
\v 29 Bulmakaun kam gumazamizibagh iniv…®ra ik…®t…®, gumazamiziba pamtem…®n an ghuavim m…®k…®mt…®, an ghuavim a is…®va d…®vazim…®n anet…®ghan koght…®, bulmakau tav m…®sueght…® an aremegham, eght…® ia kamagh…®n damu. Ia bulmakaun kam ko an ghuavim, aning m…®sueght…®, aning aremegh.  
\v 30 Eght…® gumazir araziba tuis…®zim amamangat…®gh dag…®abar ivezir d…®bobonim d…®boroght…®, gumazir kam gumazir aremezim bagh an adarazi me givezam. Arazir kam…®n bulmakaun kam arazir kuram givezegh, uaghan a uab…® angam…®ra ik…®s…® a uab…® givezam. A kamagh…®n damigh an ovengeghan kogham.  
\v 31 Bulmakaun tam, otaritam o guivitam m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, ia arazir kamra g…®n mang…®.  
\v 32 Egh bulmakaun tam ingangarir gumazim o ingangarir amizir k…®nitam m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, bulmakaun kam…®n ghuavim, 30plan silvan dag…®aba is…® ingangarir gumazim…®n gumazir dapanim dan…®ngam. Egh ia dag…®abar bulmakaun kam ginivight…®, an aremegh. 
\p  
\v 33 ‚ÄúEgh gumazitam nguazim…®n itir mozim avarazir biziba angarigh, o mozim g…®kuigh, egh anevaraghan koght…®, bulmakaun tam o donkin tam iz…® mozir kam…®n mag…®r…®gh aremegham,  
\v 34 eght…® gumazir mozim gukuizim as…®zim…®n ghuavim givezam. Egh a uab…® as…®zir kam…®n kuam iniam.  
\v 35 Eght…® gumazitam…®n bulmakau gumazir igharazim…®n bulmakau m…®sueght…® an aremeght…®, aning gumazir igharazitam…®n amamangat…®ght…®, a bulmakaun angam…®ra itir kam givesegh. Egh aning dag…®ar kaba ko bulmakaun aremezim…®n as…®ziba uaning tuiragh, uaning dan…®ngam.  
\v 36 Eght…® gumazamiziba fogh suam, bulmakaun kam an as…®zibav sozir bulmakau. An ghuavim deragh d…®vazim…®n aven a geghuvan kogh…®va, a bulmakaun angam…®ra itim is…® gumazir igharazim dan…®ngam. Egh a uab…® bulmakaun aremezim…®n as…®zim iniam.‚Äù 
\c 22  
\s1 Arazir kuraba ak…®ramin araziba 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam bulmakaun tam o sipsip tam okemegh a m…®sueght…® an aremegham, o anemadaght…® me a givezegham, eght…® ia a damight…®, a 5plan bulmakaubar bulmakaun kam ikaragham, o a 4plan sipsipbar sipsip…®n kam ikaragham.  
\v 2-4 Kamagh…®n a deraghv…®ra da ikarvagham. A ikarvaghamin bulmakauba o sipsipba puvat…®ght…®, ia aneteght…®, gumazir igharazitam ingangarir gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n a givezeght…®, ia dag…®ar kaba inigh as…®zir an okemezir kam ikarvagham. Egh an okemezir bulmakau o donki o sipsip an dafarim…®n ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, a pumuning…®n ivezim uam a gis…®n aning inigh uan ok…®mak…®am ikarvagham. 
\p ‚ÄúOk…®mak…®ar gumazim d…®magarim…®n d…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n aven mang…®s…® damut…®, d…®penim…®n ghuavim an suiragh, a m…®sueght…® an aremegham, eght…® gumazir kam os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®gham. An aruem…®n a m…®suegh…®va egh os…®mt…®zim ikiam. 
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúGumazitam uan bulmakauba ateght…® da mang…® an nguazim ko an wain…®n azenim…®n tintinibar daru dam…®va, m…®taghniam…®n ikiavk…®nigh gumazir igharazim…®n azenim…®n daghebar ameght…®, bulmakaubar ghuavim uan azenim…®n dagher aghuariba da ikarvagham. Egh uaghan wain…®n ov…®ziba gumazir kam ikarvagh a dan…®ngam.\f + \fr 22:5 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúGumazitam uan dadam daboroght…® avim isi bar ekevegh mang…®, m…®taghniam…®n ikiavk…®nigh gumazir igharazim…®n wit…®n azenim, o wit…®n me d…®ghora pozim m…®k…®nizibar isight…®, gumazir avim at…®zir kam, bizir isizir kaba bar da ikarvagham.  
\v 7 Gumazitam dag…®ataba o bizir igharazitaba is…® uan namakam danight…® a dar gan ik…®t…®, ok…®mak…®ar gumazitam bizir kaba okemegham, g…®n me ok…®mak…®ar gumazim…®n suiraght…®, ok…®mak…®ar gumazir kam bizir pumuning pumuning…®n dag…®aba ko bizir an okemeziba ikarvagham. 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúEgh me ok…®mak…®ar gumazim inighan koght…®, ia gumazir bizibar garim inigh na bagh iz…® anet…®ght…®, a nan damazim…®n m…®t…®gh. Egh a kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòK…® guizbang…®ra, bizir kaba okemezir puvat…®.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúEgh dughiaba zurara gumazitam uan namakam ko bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®gh uaning adogham. Aning bulmakauba, donkiba, sipsipba, korotiaba o bizir igharazibagh n…®ghn…®gh, uaning m…®k…®m…®va tav suam, ‚ÄòKar nan bizimra,‚Äô eght…® ia aning inigh iz…®t…® aning nan damazim…®n tught…® k…® aning baragh suam, kav ifari. Eght…® gumazir ifarir kam bizir pumuning pumuning ikarvagh namakam dan…®ngam. 
\p  
\v 10 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazitam donki, bulmakau, sipsip, ko as…®zir igharazitam, a is…® uan namakatam dan…®ngight…® ana bagh a damuam. Eght…® as…®zir kam os…®mt…®zitam a batogham, o an ovegham, o apaniba uariv sogh m…®dorozim…®n tong…®n as…®zir kam modogh a inigh mang…®ght…®, gumazitam an ganighan kogham.  
\v 11 Egh aning na bagh iz…® nan damazim…®n m…®t…®gh, egh namakar as…®zim…®n garim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam a d…®pon suam, ‚ÄòBar guizbang…®ra, k…® n…®n as…®zitam gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®gha, tam okemezir puvat…®.‚Äô Eght…® as…®zim…®n ghuavim an m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregh ifuegham. Eght…® an namakar kam as…®zir ovengezir kam ikarvaghan kogham.  
\v 12 Eght…® ok…®mak…®ar gumazitam as…®zir kam okemeght…®, namakar kam, an as…®zim ikarvagh ivezim as…®zir ghuavim dan…®ngam.  
\v 13 As…®zir atiatam as…®zir kam m…®sueght…®, namakam as…®zir tuzir dughoraghirezir tam o agharir tam inigh namakam…®n akagham. Eght…® ana as…®zir kam ikarvaghs…® dag…®atabar an…®ngan kogham. 
\p  
\v 14 ‚ÄúGumazitam uan bulmakau ateght…® an namakam ingangarim bagh a inight…®, egh dughiar bulmakaun ghuavim itir puvat…®zim…®n, bulmakaun kam os…®mt…®zim batogham o ana aremeght…®, gumazir kam as…®zim…®n ghuavim givezam.  
\v 15 Eght…® bulmakaun ghuavim uan namakam ko ik…®t…®, bulmakau os…®mt…®zim batoght…® namakam a givezan kogham. Egh namakam faragh dag…®ar akuatam ingangarim bagh bulmakau inight…®, bulmakau os…®mt…®zim batoght…® an a givezan kogham. Guizbang…®ra, dag…®ar a faragha an…®ngizim ana givezegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\s1 God me m…®geir arazir maba 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 22:16-17 \xt God…®n Araziba 22:28-29\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam guivir igiam…®n garima, a gumaziba ko akuizir puvat…®z…®, me gumazitam bagha a ginabazir puvat…®, gumazir kam a inigh a gakaghonegh a ko dakuigh…®va, gumazir kam an ik…®s…® ivezim is…® guivim…®n afeziam givezegh…®va, amizir kam…®n ikiam.  
\v 17 Eght…® guivir kam…®n afeziam gumazir kam…®n aghuaght…®, gumazir kam uab…® dag…®aba is…® amizim…®n afeziam givezam. Ivezir kam…®n d…®bobonim, a ivezir amizim gumazitam ko akuizir puvat…®zim…®n m…®n ikiam. 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 22:18 \xt God…®n Araziba 18:10-11\x*‚ÄúIa imezibagh amir amizibav sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregh. 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 22:19 \xt Ofa Gami 18:23; 20:15-16; God…®n Araziba 27:21\x*‚ÄúGumazitam, amizim ko akuir arazim, as…®zir amebatam ko a damight…®, ia a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Amizitam, gumazim ko akuir arazim, as…®zir apurim ko a damight…®, ia a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. 
