\v 20 \x - \xo 22:20 \xt God…®n Araziba 17:2-7\x*‚ÄúEght…® tav asem bagh ofa damigh egh an ziam feght…®, ia a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God baghv…®ra ofa damu, egh an ziamra f…®. 
