\v 21 \x - \xo 22:21-22 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:9; Ofa Gami 19:33-34; God…®n Araziba 24:17-18; 27:19\x*‚ÄúIa kantrin igharazim…®n gumazir ia ko ititam paz…®va a damuan mark…®, egh os…®mt…®zim a dar…®ghan kogham. Ia fo, ia faragha an m…®n kamagh…®ra Isip…®n kantrin ike.  
\v 22 Ia paz…®va amizir pam aremezim damuan mark…®, egh uaghan borir afeziam aremezim paz…®va a damuan mark…®.  
\v 23 Ia paz…® me damut…®, me akurvazim bagh na bagh arangt…®, k…® men d…®mdiam baragham.  
\v 24 Egh k…® navim ikuvigh, gumazir kurabar amight…®, me iz…® ia m…®soght…®, ia ar…®m…®ghiregham. Kamagh…®n, ia uaghan amuiba paba puvat…®gham, eght…® ian boriba afeziaba puvat…®gham. 
