\v 25 \x - \xo 22:25 \xt Ofa Gami 25:35-38; God…®n Araziba 15:7-11; 23:19-20\x*‚ÄúNan gumazamizir dag…®aba ko biziba bar puvat…®ziba, men tav ia da dag…®ataba inight…® ia me dan…®ng n…®ghn…®gh suam, a g…®n ua ia ikarvagham. Ia gumazir dag…®ar ingangaribagh amibar m…®n, gumazir kaba da, dag…®ar kaba ua da iniva, dag…®ataba uam a gis…®n dar…®ghan mark…®, Bar mark…®.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 22:26-27 \xt God…®n Araziba 24:10-13\x*Gumazir tam ian dag…®aba inigh uan korotiar azenim…®n azuim is…® ia dan…®ng m…®k…®m suam, korotiar kam kamagh…®n ian aka, a g…®n dag…®ar kaba ua da ikaragham. Eght…® ia uam an korotiar azenan azuim, dughiar kamra aruem t…®ghar mag…®ram, ia uam a dan…®ngigh.  
\v 27 Guizbang…®ra, a bar korotiar azenim…®n azuir kamra iti. Egh d…®magarim…®n a fefem a dan…®ngt…®, an arugharughan kogham. Eght…® n…® korotiar azenim…®n azuir ruarim…®n suiraght…®, a bizir tizim…®n uan m…®karzim avaragh dakuam? K…® gumazamiziba bar men apangkufi. Kamagh…®n, gumazir kam uab…®n akurvaghs…® na m…®k…®mt…®, k…® an m…®g…®r…®g…®am baragham. 
\p  
\v 28 \x - \xo 22:28 \xt Aposel 23:5\x*‚ÄúIa God, akar kuraba a m…®k…®man kogham. Egh ia akar kuratam uan gumazir dapanitam m…®k…®man kogh, an ziam gas…®ghas…®ghan kogham. 
\p  
\v 29 ‚ÄúIa uan wit…®n faragha zuiba, ko wain…®n d…®par faragha zuiba, ko oliv…®n borer faragha zuiba, ia nan anogoroghan mark…®. Egh ia da inigh ofan m…®n nan ziam f…®s…® na dan…®ng. Egh ia uan otarir ivariaba na dan…®ng.  
\v 30 Ia uaghan uan bulmakaun faragha otiviziba ko sipsip…®n faragha otiviziba na bagh ofa damu. Bulmakaun nguzim ko sipsip…®n nguzim 7plan aruebar uan amebam ko ikeght…®, namba 8…®n dughiam, ia a m…®suegh…®va na bagh ofa damuam.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 22:31 \xt Ofa Gami 17:15\x*Guizbang…®ra, ia nan gumazamizibara. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, as…®zir atiatam m…®sogha dughoraghsuezir as…®zim, ia an tuzitam aman mark…®. Ia an tuziba is…® afiabar an…®ng.‚Äù 
\c 23  
\s1 Israelia arazir aghuaribara damu 
