\v 1 \x - \xo 23:1 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:16; Ofa Gami 19:11-12; God…®n Araziba 5:20\x*Moses Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam kamagh…®n anekuri, ‚ÄúN…® bizir otozitam baraghiz…®, a guiz…®n akam puvat…®, n…® bizir kam tintinibar a m…®k…®man mark…®. Gumazitam arazir kuratam damight…®, os…®mt…®zim an ik…®t…®, n…® kot…®n aven akar ifavaribav k…®m…®va an akurvaghan mark…®.  
\v 2 Gumazir av…®riba arazir kurabar amut…®, n…® men arazibar g…®n mangan mark…®. Eght…® gumazir av…®riba kotiam…®n mang…®va, kotiam gifaramin m…®g…®r…®g…®abav k…®mt…®, n…® men arazir kabar g…®n mangan mark…®.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 23:3 \xt Ofa Gami 19:15\x*Gumazitaba gumazir biziba puvat…®zim kotiam dat…®ght…®, a uab…®n akurvaghs…® n…® inight…®, n…® gumazir biziba puvat…®zim…®n akurvaghs…® ifavarir m…®g…®r…®g…®abav k…®man mark…®. 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 23:4-5 \xt God…®n Araziba 22:1-4\x*‚ÄúEght…® n…®n apanim…®n donki o bulmakau d…®vazim ategh pura darut…®, n…® an ganigh, uam a inigh gumazir kam bagh mang…®.  
\v 5 N…® gumazir ian aghuazim…®n donkin gant…®, a bizir os…®mt…®ziba ater ir…®gh…®v ik…®t…®, n…® gumazir kam…®n akuragh uam an donki ghufegh. N…® aneteght…® a nguazim…®n ir…®gh…®v ikian mark…®.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 23:6-8 \xt Ofa Gami 19:15; God…®n Araziba 16:19\x*Gumazir biziba puvat…®zitam kotiam…®n mang…®t…®, ia kotiam…®n aven a gifar…®va a d…®kab…®nan mark…®.  
\v 7 N…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ifavaribar gumazim gas…®va a is…® kotiam dar…®ghan mark…®. Egh gumazir aghuarim arazir kuratam damighan koght…®, ia is…® kotiam dat…®gh…®va, n…® puram a m…®sueght…® an aremeghan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, gumazir arazir kurar kam gamim, an os…®mt…®zim ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…® k…® a is…® kotiam dat…®ght…®, an ovengam.  
\v 8 Gumazitam ia apezeper kotiam gifar…®s…®va dag…®aba ia dan…®ngt…®, ia dag…®ar kaba inian mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, arazir kam gumazir dapanibar damaziba ap…®riz…® me derav…®ra n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Egha arazir kam uaghan gumazir aghuarir os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®zibar kotiam gas…®ghas…®si.  
