\v 22 Ia an akam…®n g…®n mang…®gh, egh bizir k…® m…®kemezibar amight…®, k…® ian apanibar apanim…®n m…®n otogh me m…®sogham. Eght…® gumazir ia adogha ia batoziba, k…® me adogh me batuegham.  
