\v 1 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® kamaghsua, N…®, Aron, Nadap, Abihu, ko Israelian gumazir 70plan gumazir dapaniba, ia m…®ghs…®am…®n anang na bagh iz…®. Egh ia tong saghon ik…®va, tevimning ap…®righ guam nguazim…®n aneb…®ragh nan ziam f…®.  
