\v 17 \x - \xo 25:17 \xt Hibru 9:5\x*‚ÄúEgh ia Boksiam…®n asuam gol…®n aghuarim…®n an ingaright…®, an ruarim 110 sentimitan tught…®, an arozim 66 sentimitan tugh. Danganir kam, kar gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin danganim.  
