\v 27 Egh ia gol ring…®n pumuning uam aning…®n ingarigh, egh aning is…® korotiar otevir ivariam…®n amadaghan itim…®n, azenan aning porogh aning isamigh. Egh aning ikeght…®, aning…®n otevimning d…®p…®zimning…®n ikegha izighir…® inir ruarir ivariam gikezim…®n tugh. Egh ivariam gikezir inir me deraghav…®ra kurkezir kam an borogh…®n, gol ringning isamigh.  
\v 28 Egh benir sazir blupla inigh, evarim…®n ikiamin forivtarir inim…®n ringning is…®, korotiar otevir azenan itim…®n ringning gikegh, eght…® evarim…®n itir forivtarir inim, korotiar otevir azenan itim…®n suiragh gavgavight…®, evarim…®n ikiamin forivtarir inim ighuamangan kogham. 
\p  
\v 29 ‚ÄúEgh Aron Anogoroghezir Danganir kam…®n aven mangamin dughiar kam…®n, a forivtarir inir Israelian ovavibar ziaba aven itim inigh uan evarim…®n borogh…®n uan evarim gikegh. Kar God…®n ifongiam g…®foghamin bizim. Eght…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n ganigh, egh k…® uan gumazamiziba zurara me g…®n…®ghn…®gham.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 28:30 \xt D…®boboniba 27:21; God…®n Araziba 33:8; Esra 2:63; Nehemia 7:65\x*Egh dag…®ar God…®n ifongiam g…®fofoghamin kamning is…®, forivtarir inir an evarim…®n itim darugh, eght…® aning an evarim gis…®rara ikiam. Eght…® Aron Anogoroghezir Danganim…®n mang…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n tuivs…®, a dag…®ar kamning inigh aning sara mang…®. Egh Israelia God…®n ifongiam g…®foghs…®, Aron dag…®ar kamning uan forivtarir inim darugh, uan evarim gis…®rara aning ater Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n tuivam.‚Äù 
\s1 Me ofa gamir gumaziba bagh  // korotiar igharazitabar ingaram 
