\v 27 ‚ÄúAron ofa gamir gumazim…®n otivs…®, n…® sipsip…®n evarir tuzim uan dafarim…®n an suiragh a fegh a damut…® a nan damazim…®n ighuavamang…®. Egh Aron…®n otariba bagh sipsip…®n buarak…®rir agharir guvim…®n itim inigh uan dafarim…®n an suiragh a fegh a damut…® a nan damazim…®n ighuavamang…®. Arazir kam…®n, n…® ofa gamir gumazibar ik…®s…® me am…®sefegh. Egh g…®n ia as…®zir tuzir kam is…® ofa gamir gumazibar an…®ngight…®, me anerem…®.  
\v 28 Egh dughiaba Israelia zurara na ko navir vam…®ra ik…®s…®, as…®zir evarim…®n itim ko buaragharim inigh, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God na dan…®ng. Eght…® k…® ofa gamir gumazibar an…®ngight…®, me aneremam. Bizir k…® damuasa m…®kemezir kam ik…®v…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 29 ‚ÄúEght…® g…®n Aron aremeght…®, me an ofa gamir gumazim…®n korotiar aghuarim is…® an otaribar an…®ngigh. Eght…® Aron…®n ik…®zim…®n adarazi ofa gamir gumazibar otivs…®, me korotiar kam arught…®, me me am…®s…®va borem me gingam.  
\v 30 Eght…® Aron…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazitam an danganim inigh ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n otivs…®, egh a faragh korotiar kabar aghuigh na bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven mang…®va Anogoroghezir Danganim…®n aven nan ingangarim damu mang…® 7plan dughiabar tugham. 
\p  
\v 31 ‚ÄúDughiar n…® Aron ko an otariba m…®s…®vamim, n…® sipsip…®n tuzir n…® ofa gamizim inigh, na baghav…®ra itir Purirpenim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven a is…® m…®nem darugh anevikigh.  
\v 32 Eght…® Aron ko an otariba, sipsip…®n tuzir kam ko bret…®n ak…®ram…®n ikiav…®ra itim inigh, egh na bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n anerem…®.  
\v 33 Me ofa gamir gumaziba am…®s…®vamin dughiam…®n, me uan arazir kuraba g…®n amangasa ofa gamua tuezir dagher kaba me dar am…®. Dagher kaba na baghav…®ra ikiava bar anogoroke. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ofa gamir gumazibara dagher kabar amam, eght…® gumazamizir k…®niba bar puvat…®gham.  
\v 34 Egh as…®zir tuzitaba ko bret…®n ik…® mang…®t…® am…®nim tiraghamba, ia dar aman mark…®. As…®zir tuzir kamagh amizim na baghav…®ra ikia bar anogoroke, kamagh me avim…®n a tuaght…® a bar is…® m…®gh…®righ puvat…®gh. 
\p  
\v 35 ‚ÄúEgh k…® n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, n…® Aron uan otariba ko me am…®s…®v…®s…®, ingangarir kam damu mang…®t…®, namba 7…®n dughiam otogh.  
\v 36 Dughiabar zurara n…® arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…®, bulmakaun vam…®ran ofan m…®n ofa damu. Eght…® ofan kam ofa gamir dakozim damight…® a nan damazim bar zuegham. Egh oliv…®n borem is…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n a fugh, anem…®seveght…® a nan ofa gamir dakozimra ikiam.  
