\p  
\v 38 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa dughiaba vaghvagh sipsip…®n nguzir azenir vam…®ra itir pumuning inigh, egh ofa gamir dakozim…®n dar ofa damu.  
\v 39 Ia m…®zarazim…®n sipsip…®n kamning…®n tam is…® an ofa damu. Egh bar guarat…®zim…®n, ia tam…®n ofa damu.  
\v 40 Egh ia wit…®n ingarizir 1 kilogrem plauan aghuitam inigh, 1 lita oliv…®n borem sara aning veregh, egh sipsip…®n faragha ofa gamir kam ko ofa damu. Egh uaghan 1 lita wain…®n d…®pam inigh, ofan m…®n afugh.  
\v 41 Egh ia guarat…®zim…®n sipsip…®n igharazim inigh, an ofa damu. Egh ia m…®zarazim…®n amizir ofan m…®rara ofa damu, egh ia wit tuamin ofa ko, wain…®n d…®pam…®n ofa inigh, ofa damu. Eght…® dagher ia ofan m…®n avim…®n tuez…® m…®gh…®rizir kam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ofan kam…®n mughuriam baregh, egh a gifuegh navir aghuim an ikiam.  
\v 42 Eght…® ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rir kam, ian g…®n otivamin ovavir boriba zurara dughiabar na bativamin Purirpenim…®n tiar akam…®n ofa damu, eght…® k…® an ganam. Eght…® k…® uan gumazamiziba danganir kam…®n ia bativam. K…® danganir kamra n…® ko m…®k…®mam.  
\v 43 Eght…® nan angazangarir ekiam ko gavgavim Purirpenim…®n otiv, egh danganir kam damight…®, a nan danganim…®n m…®n otogham. Eght…® k…® danganir kam…®n Israelian gumazamiziba bativam.  
\v 44 Egh k…®, na bativamin Purirpenim ko ofa gamir dakozim am…®seveght…®, aning nan bizimning…®n m…®n ikiam. Eght…® k…® Aron uan otariba ko me am…®seveght…®, me ofa gamir gumazibar m…®n nan ingangarim damuam.  
\v 45 Eght…® k…® Israelia ian tong…®n ik…®, egh ian God…®n ikiam.  
\v 46 Eght…® ia deraghv…®ra fogham, k…®rara k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ian God, egha k…®rara Isip…®n kantrin ia inigha ian akua ize. Ez…® kamagh…®n k…® ian tong…®n ikiam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, egha k…® uab…® k…® ian God.‚Äù 
\c 30  
\s1 Me pauran mughuriar aghuim tuamin ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingaram 
\r (Ua Me Ini 37:25-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa akas…®n temem inigh ofa gamir dakozir tam…®n ingarigh. Dakozir kam, ia pauran aghuarim tuaght…® a m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim otivam.  
\v 2 Eght…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n ruarim 45 sentimitan tugh, eght…® an arozim an ruarim…®n m…®rara mang…® 45 sentimitan tugh, eght…® an tuirivim 90 sentimitan tugh. Egh temer akas…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingarizimra, ia bulmakaun kombar m…®n garir bizibar ingaright…®, da ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®kebaba vaghvagh dar ik…®.  
\v 3 Egh an 4plan m…®riaba, ko an siriam, ko an komba, ia gol…®n aghuarim…®n dar puegh da nokegh. Egh gol…®n ruarim is…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®riabar ar…®gh…®va dagh ighuigh.  
\v 4 Egh gol ring…®n pumuning…®n ingarigh, tam is…® vong…®n a ikegh, egh vong…®n tam ikegh. Ia ring…®n kamning is…® gol…®n ruarir an m…®riabar ikeghamim…®n apengan aning ikegh. Ring…®n kamning ofa gamir dakozim aters…® tememning aning daghuam.  
\v 5 Ia akas…®n iter pumuning inigh ofa gamir dakozim aters…® aning ak…®righ, egh gol…®n aning nokegh.  
\v 6 Egh ofa gamir dakozir kam is…®, inir ekiar Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam modozim…®n azenan anet…®gh. Boksiar kam gis…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amadir danganim iti. Eght…® danganir arazir kuraba g…®n amadir kam…®n, k…® ia bativam. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúEgh zurara m…®zarazibar Aron iz…®va lamba ak…®rm…®gh, egh dughiar kamra pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim ofa gamir dakozir kam…®n da tu, egh m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim damut…® an otivam.  
\v 8 Egh a guarat…®zibar lamba ak…®rm…®gh, egh pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim…®n ofa damu. Egh ofan kam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, na bagh a damu, egh zurara g…®n izamin dughiabar kamagh…®ra damu.  
\v 9 Ia pauran mughuriar aghuir igharazitabar ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim dakozir kam…®n da tuan mark…®, as…®ziba tuan mark…®, witba tuan mark…®, wain inian mark…®, bizir kaba k…® ian anogoroke.  
\v 10 Egh azeniba bar dughiar vam…®ra,\f + \fr 30:10 \ft Azeniba bar dughiar vam…®ra, kar Dughiar Ekiar Gumazamizibar Arazir Kuraba G…®n Amadim. N…® Ofa Gami, sapta 16…®n gan.\f* Aron ofa gamir dakozir kam nan damazim…®n zueghs…®, ingangarim damuam. Ingangarir kam kamak…®n: As…®zir ian arazir kuraba g…®n amangasa ofa gamim, Aron an ghuzitam inigh, ofa gamir dakozir kam…®n kombar ar…®kigh. Ia arazir kam zurara azenibar a damu. Ofa gamir dakozir bar zuezir kam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kar nan bizimra.‚Äù 
\s1 Purirpenim bagh dag…®aba iniamin arazim 
\p  
\v 11-12 Egha g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Israelian gumazibar ziaba ak…®nafarim…®n da osiramin dughiam, gumaziba bar vaghvagh uan ik…®r…®m…®rim uam a inis…® dag…®ar taba na dan…®ng. Puvat…®ght…®, ar…®mariar ekiar kuram otogh, dughiar kam…®n me gas…®ghasigham.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 30:13 \xt Ua Me Ini 38:25-26; Matyu 17:24\x*Eght…® gumazir me ziaba iniziba, me bar 5 kinan silvan dag…®aba is…® ofan m…®n na dan…®ngam.  
\v 14 Egh me 20plan azenibar ikegha ghuavanadir gumazibar ziaba iniam, eght…® me bar dag…®ar kaba na dan…®ngam.  
\v 15 Eght…® dag…®aba itir gumaziba av…®ribar an…®ngan mark…®, eght…® dag…®aba puvat…®zir gumaziba dag…®ar muziaribar an…®ngan mark…®. Me bar 5 kina na dan…®ng, egh me uan arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin ivezim…®n m…®n a givesegh, egh me aremeghan kogham.  
\v 16 Eght…® n…® dag…®ar kam is…® na bativamin Purirpenim…®n ganamin ingarim damu. Eght…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, dag…®ar kabar gan fogh suam, ‚ÄòKar me uan arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin ivezim, kamagh…®n k…® Israelian gumazamiziba bak…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\s1 Ofa gamir gumaziba uan soroghafariba ruer itarir ekiam 
\p  
\v 17-18 \x - \xo 30:17-18 \xt Ua Me Ini 38:8\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bras…®n taba inigh soroghafariba ruer itarir ekiatam ko anefamin dakozim…®n ingarigh. Egh dakozim is…® ofa gamir dakozim ko na bativamin Purirpenim…®n t…®zim…®n anet…®gh. Egh itarir ekiam dakozim…®n p…®n anefagh, egh d…®pam itarir ekiam gingegh.  
\v 19 Eght…® Aron uan otariba ko, me uan soroghafariba ruam.  
\v 20 Egh me na bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven mang…®s…®, o ofaba isia m…®gh…®ri nagh…®n dakozim…®n ofa damus…®, me uan soroghafariba rueght…® k…® me m…®sueght…® me aremeghan kogham.  
\v 21 Bar guizbang…®ra, me uan soroghafariba ruegh, egh me aremeghan kogham. Me ko, men otarir g…®n otivamiba, me zurara bizir k…® damuasa m…®kemezibar g…®n mang…®v…®ra ik…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Ofa gamir gumaziba m…®sevir borem…®n ingarir arazim 
\p  
\v 22-23 \x - \xo 30:22-38 \xt Ua Me Ini 37:29\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bizir aghuarir mughuriar aghuim itiba, da inigh: Mean sanda, an os…®mt…®zim 6 kilogrem, ko sinamon…®n pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim, an os…®mt…®zim 3 kilogrem, ko abuar mughuriar aghuim zuim, an os…®mt…®zim 3 kilogrem.  
\v 24-25 Egh pauran me iter kasian inim…®n ingarizim, an os…®mt…®zim 6 kilogrem, a inigh. Egh 4 lita oliv…®n borem inigh, bizir kaba bar dagh ingegh. Egha mati gumazir fofozir bar aghuim ikia derav…®ra sandaba verez…® mogh…®n, n…® deraghv…®ra da vereght…® sandan aghuim otogham. Borer kam, an ingangarim kamak…®n: me bizim o gumazim na bagh anem…®s…®v…®s…®, borer kam is…® a gingegh. 
\p  
\v 26 ‚ÄúEgh n…® borer aghuarir kam is…® na bativamin Purirpenim gingegh, egh Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam gingegh,  
\v 27 egh bretba ar…®ghamin dakozim ko an ingarir bizibagh ingegh, egh lamba afamin aghorim, ko an ingarir biziba sara, dagh ingegh, egh pauran mughuriar aghuim tuamin ofa gamir dakozim gingegh,  
\v 28 egh as…®ziba da bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim ko, an ingangarir bizibagh ingegh, egh soroghafariba ruamin itarir ekiam ko anefamin dakozim gingegh.  
\v 29 Egh n…® bizir kaba m…®seveght…® da bar nan biziba, egh bar anogoregham. Eght…® gumazitam o bizitam a seregham, egh a uaghan na baghv…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 30 ‚ÄúEght…® g…®n Aron ko an otariba, me am…®s…®v…®s…®, ia borer kam inigh muziaritam me gingegh. Eght…® me nan ofa gamir gumazibar otogh nan ingangarim damuam.  
\v 31 Eght…® n…® kamagh…®n Israelian gumazamizibav k…®m, ‚ÄòIa ko ian adarazir g…®n izamiba, ia oliv…®n borer kam inigh na baghv…®ra ikiamin biziba am…®s…®vam.  
\v 32 Egh ia gumazir k…®nibar ingan mark…®. Egh ia uaghan borer kamagh…®ra garir tam uari bagh an ingaran mark…®. Kar God…®n bizimra, k…® ian anogoroke.  
\v 33 Eght…® gumazir borer kam is…® pura gumazir k…®nitam gingeghamim, ko gumazir borer kamagh…®ra garibar ingariba, gumazir kamagh…®n amir kaba, nan gumazamizibar ik…®zim…®n aven ikian kogham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\s1 M…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim…®n pauran ingaramin arazim 
\p  
\v 34 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua Moses kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim…®n pauran ingars…®, pauran mughuriar aghuim zuir igharagha garitaba inigh, eght…® pauran kabar os…®mt…®ziba vorogh…®ra mang…®. Pauran kabanang: mean paura, ko pauran me zoghuabar m…®n garir bizim…®n ingarizim, ko galbanum…®n ak…®marim…®n eborir gavgavim…®n, ko pauran me iter balsam…®n eborim…®n ingarizim, bar da inigh,  
\v 35 egh deraghv…®ra da vereght…®, mati gumazir fofozir aghuim itim, pauran mughuriar aghuim…®n ingari. Egh amangs…®zir muziaritam at…®ght…®, paura derav…®ram otogham. Egh a bar nan bizimra, k…® ian anogoroke.  
\v 36 Egh deraghv…®ra pauran kam…®n taba m…®rm…®right…®, an averenim…®n m…®n guiz…®n pauran otogh. Eght…® a inigh na bativamin Purirpenim…®n aven nan damazim…®n mang…®, Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n borogh…®n anet…®gh. Eght…® pauran mughuriar aghuim zuir kam, a nan bizimra, k…® ian anogoroke.  
\v 37 Eght…® ia pauran kamagh…®n gari tam uari bagh an ingaran mark…®. Kar k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan bizimra, k…® ian anogoroke.  
\v 38 Eght…® gumazitam sandan mughuriar aghuim baraghs…® ifuegh…®va, a kamagh…®ra garir bizitam…®n ingarigh, egh a nan gumazamizibar ik…®zim…®n aven ikian kogham.‚Äù 
\c 31  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan Purirpenim…®n bizibar ingarasa gumaziba am…®sefe 
\r (Ua Me Ini 35:30-31) 
\p  
\v 1 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God Judan anabam…®n gumazim Besalel am…®sevegha g…®fa, a Urin otarim, egha a Hur…®n igiar borim.  
\v 3-4 K…® uan Duam…®n gavgavim a gan…®ngi. Egha k…® gol, silva, ko bras…®n bizir aghuir igharazibar ingaramin fofozir aghuim ko ingangarir aghuibar amuamin n…®ghn…®zim a gan…®ngi.  
\v 5 Egha k…® dag…®ar ivezim bar p…®n koziba aghor…®va, temebar dirir guar av…®ribar aghor, egh Purirpenim as…®ngamin ingangarir av…®ribar fofozir aghuiba a gan…®ngi.  
\v 6 Egha k…® uaghan Ahisamak…®n otarim Oholiap am…®sevegha g…®fa, me Dan…®n anabam…®n adarasi, eght…® a uaghan Besalel ko ingaram. Egha k…® uaghan fofozir ekiam gumazir igharazibagh an…®ngi, eght…® k…® n…® m…®kemezir biziba, me bar dar ingaram.  
\v 7 Egh me na bativamin Purirpenim…®n ingar, egh Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam…®n ingar, egh Boksiam…®n asuam, kar arazir kuraba g…®n amadir danganim, an ingar, egh Purirpenim…®n biziba bar dar ingaram.  
\v 8 Egh me bretba ar…®ghamin dakozim ko an ingarir biziba bar dar ingar, egh lamba afamin aghorim ko lam ko an ingaramin biziba bar dar ingar. Me gol…®n aghuarimra lamba afamin aghorir kam…®n ingarigh. Egh me uaghan pauran mughuriar aghuim tuamin ofa gamir dakozim…®n ingarigh.  
\v 9 Egh me as…®ziba bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofa gamir dakozim ko, ofan ingangarim gamir biziba bar dar ingar. Egh me soroghafariba ruer itarir ekiam ko anefamin dakozim…®n ingar.  
\v 10 Egh me Aron uan otariba ko, me bagh ofa gamir gumazibar korotiar aghuaribara isamight…® me dar aghuigh, egh ofa gamir gumazim…®n ingangarim damuam.  
\v 11 Egh oliv…®n borer k…® ua bagha m…®sevezir bizibagh ingem…®n ingar, egh pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim Anogoroghezir Danganim bagh an ingarigh. Eght…® me ingarir bizir kaba, k…® n…® m…®kemez mogh…®ra me dar amu.‚Äù 
\s1 Sabat…®n dughiam,  // kar avughsamin dughiam 
\p  
\v 12-13 \x - \xo 31:12-13 \xt Esekiel 20:12; 20:20\x*Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®k…®masa kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúSabat…®n dughiam, kar dughiar avughsamim. Kamagh…®n ia zurara Sabat…®n dughiam…®n avughs…®. Sabat…®n dughiam, an ababanim…®n m…®n k…® ia gan…®di, a dat…®r…®gh…®n ko ian adarazir dughiar g…®n izamibar ababanim…®n m…®n ikiam. Ababanir kam ian akaght…® ia fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ia gamiz…® ia nan gumazamizibar m…®rara iti.  
\v 14 Ez…® dughiar avughsamin kam, kar k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan dughiamra, kamagh…®n ia an avughs…®. Gumazitam dughiar kam…®n ingangaritam damight…®, ia a m…®sueght…® an aremegh. Gumazir kamagh…®n ami, nan gumazamizibar ik…®zim…®n aven ikian kogham.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 31:15 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:8-11; 23:12; 34:21; 35:2; Ofa Gami 23:3; God…®n Araziba 5:12-14\x*Ia wigh…®n vam…®ran an 6plan dughiabar ingangaribar amu, namba 7…®n dughiam, kar nan dughiamra, kar nan avughsazir dughiar ekiam. Egh gumazir dughiar kam…®n ingangaribagh amiba, me bar me m…®sueght…®, me ar…®m…®ghiregh.  
\v 16 Kar Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir ia g…®n mangasa akam ak…®rizim, kamagh…®n, ia Israelia dughiar kam…®n avughs…® ik…®v…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® ian g…®n izamin adarazi kamagh…®ra damuam.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 31:17 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:11\x*K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® overiam ko nguazim 6plan dughiabar aning…®n ingari, egha dughiar namba 7…®n, k…® ingangariba bar da ategha avughsi. Ez…® dughiar kam, a na ko ia Israelian tizim…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gamima, an ababanim…®n m…®n oto.‚Äù  
\v 18 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Moses ko Sainain M…®ghs…®am…®n m…®kemegha g…®vagha, egha God uab…® dag…®ar akuar pumuning isa Moses gan…®ngi. God uab…® uan dafarir puzim…®n Akar Gavgaviba aning…®n da osiri. 
\c 32  
\ms1 Israelia ak…®rim ragha God gasara, egha g…®n uamategha a bagha ize 
\mr (Sapta 32--34) 
\s1 Gumazamiziba gol…®n bulmakaun nguzim…®n ingari 
\r (God…®n Araziba 9:6-29) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 32:1 \xt Aposel 7:40\x*Egha Moses dughiar ruarim…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n ikia zuam…®ra izezir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamiziba uari akuvagha iza kamagh…®n Aron m…®gei, ‚ÄúE fozir puvat…®, bizir tizimra Moses bato, gumazir kam Isip…®n kantrin e inigha en akua ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…® n…® d…®kavigh, e bagh god…®n tabar ingaright…®, da en faragh mang…®va e inigh tuavim…®n mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® Aron me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uan amuiba ko, otariba ko guivibar kuaribar guizir gol…®n ringba, da suegh da inigh na bagh iz…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Egha Aron kamagh…®n m…®kemez…®, gumazamiziba bar uan kuaribar gol…®n ringba asigha da inigha a bagha izi.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 32:4 \xt 1 Atriviba 12:28; Aposel 7:41\x*Ez…® a kuaribar guizir gol ring…®n kaba inigha, da tuez…® da isigha ameregha d…®pam ara. Ez…® an a isa mozir me bulmakaun nguzim…®n nedazim…®n m…®n nguazim…®n kuizim…®n, a fugha bulmakaun nguzim…®n ingari. Egha afuam inigha deraghav…®ra anerk…®ri. Ez…® g…®n gumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIsraelia, ia oragh. Kar en godba. Da Isip…®n kantrin e inigha, en akua azenan ize.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Aron kamagh…®n ganigha ofa gamir dakozim bulmakaun borogh…®n an ingarigha ghaze, ‚ÄúE gurumzaraghan isar ekiam ko ighiam damu, egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God ziar ekiam a dan…®ngam.‚Äù  
\v 6 \x - \xo 32:6 \xt 1 Korin 10:7\x*Egha am…®mzaraghan bar m…®zaraghara, gumazamiziba d…®kavigha iza ofan as…®ziba tue da bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofabagh ami. Egha me uaghan God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofaba inigha iza ofa gami. Egha g…®n apiagha dagheba ko d…®paba amegha, g…®n d…®kavigha ghua ighiar kurabagh ami. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® zuam…®ra mag…®r…®. Gumazamizir n…® Isip…®n inigha izeziba, me arazir kurar av…®ribagh ami.  
\v 8 Me tuavir me g…®n mangamin k…® me m…®kemezim, me zuam…®ra anetegha, gol…®n bulmakaun nguzim…®n ingarigha, an ziam fa an ofa gami. Egha me ghaze, ‚ÄòIsraelia, ia oragh, kar en godba. Da Isip…®n kantrin e inigha, en akua ize.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Moses m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamizir kaba, k…® men ganigha me g…®fo. Me gumazamizir akaba batoziba.  
\v 10 K…® me bagh navim isi bar men an…®ngaghegham. Egh k…® bar me gas…®ghasigham. Eght…® n…® nan anogoroghan kogham, bar mark…®. Egh g…®n k…® n…® ko n…®n boribar adarazir amight…®, me ik…®zir gavgavir mam…®n otogham.‚Äù 
\p  
